msgctxt "e07534ed-30a0-4368-a081-8bd37c48df3d"
msgid ""
"This helmet gives its wearer DR 2/- against ranged attacks (10/- against falling "
"and thrown rocks), and the ability to cast good hope and crushing despair spells "
"once per day (Caster level 11, DC 17). It also gives a +3 dodge bonus to AC and +3 "
"insight bonus to saving throws against the enemies of the Giant and Goblinoid "
