msgctxt "f1dc5ebb-d772-4f59-b118-b1cc66a7057b"
msgid ""
"\\\"Stop! I give up! Here's your piece of iron. Please, can I go to prison now?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"멈춰! 내가 졌어! 여기 조각을 받아. 나 이제 감옥으로 들어가면 안 될까?\\\""

msgctxt "d1557659-a89b-4324-9810-f7500b329087"
msgid ""
"\\\"That's none of my concern. It looks broken. Can't give you a coin more.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내 알 바 아니야. 부서진 것 같군. 동전 하나를 더 줄 수는 없어.\\\""

msgctxt "016f8e01-28fc-4763-a929-d88de9ddfc9f"
msgid ""
"\\\"That's a ridiculously low price for a piece like this! It's dwarven made, you "
"know! My grandfather used to wear it!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"이런 물건이 이렇게 싸다니 말도 안 돼! 이건 드워프가 만든 것이라고! 내 할아버지"
"가 사용하시고는 했지!\\\""

msgctxt "af225d23-cb28-4ef7-8a29-2c648bf833fd"
msgid "\\\"I'm returning the armor to you. You may finish your work.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이 갑옷을 돌려주겠어. 하던 일을 마무리 해.\\\""

msgctxt "22c05843-f4c0-42f4-a538-6eec1ab27406"
msgid "\\\"Kergan told me your family didn't treat him very well.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"Kergan이 말하길 네 가족이 위협하지는 않았다는군.\\\""

msgctxt "f5cea330-3110-464a-81a9-9668082b756a"
msgid "Exiled Dragn for riding roughshod over his brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "836363f9-e2ec-405c-ab74-a0ae6445c8e0"
msgid "\\\"You're a tyrant, lording over your brother. Go away.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이 반역자야. 네 형제를 싣고 가라. 꺼져.\\\""

msgctxt "b0f660d7-b8e5-405c-8596-8db29dd5751d"
msgid "\\\"This is your private family matter. I won't interfere.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이건 너희 가족 문제야. 나는 상관하지 않겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "5a809316-07e3-4389-9a23-6c00a873f2b5"
msgid "\\\"Who robbed you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"누가 너를 강탈했지?\\\""

msgctxt "cb1252ed-7d18-4c0a-9dca-7a05f7a43e3e"
msgid "\\\"I recovered your grandfather's armor. You can take it.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 할아버지의 갑옷을 고쳤다. 가져가.\\\""

msgctxt "f4db1fb3-24b9-4f35-b807-3bb953ccf750"
msgid "\\\"Remind me where I can find the merchants who might have your armor.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 갑옷을 사줄 상인이 어디에 있는지 알려줘.\\\""

msgctxt "7b502fa3-28de-4b1e-9d46-ff8b0936ba4f"
msgid ""
"\\\"So tell me about that idea you had about a family relic and a masterpiece…\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너의 가보와 보물에 대해 말해줘...\\\""

msgctxt "a4cd4c45-dd80-4930-b2eb-552a2af4eedf"
msgid "\\\"I want to know more about you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에 대해 더 알고 싶다.\\\""

msgctxt "38ba1128-e98a-455a-a80c-e014eb91ea43"
msgid "\\\"I'm in a hurry. We'll talk later.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나는 바빠. 다음에 얘기하지.\\\""

msgctxt "b70f60dc-4a98-44bd-bc0d-95f9d89d540a"
msgid "\\\"What has led you to these lands?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이 땅에 온 이유는 뭐지?\\\""

msgctxt "26720154-d4e1-4e18-a256-0fe5caa1abdb"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about your craft.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 재주에 대해 말해봐.\\\""

msgctxt "7bdc175a-e834-4f0a-9499-92bc1b4c6fb3"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about your family.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 가족에 대해 말해봐.\\\""

msgctxt "905320b7-e371-4f8b-8088-358295dafbac"
msgid "\\\"We'll discuss this later.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"다음에 이야기하지.\\\""

msgctxt "9a468880-cf40-47f3-884c-3eec85df9831"
msgid "\\\"Do you like it in my lands?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내 땅은 마음에 드나?\\\""

msgctxt "7c4349ab-dded-482b-ae65-a5b446b0ede5"
msgid ""
"\\\"Kergan wants me to tell you that he doesn't give a damn about you and your "
"hammers.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"Kergan이 말하길 너 따위는 상관하지 않는다는군.\\\""

msgctxt "cbc7ec0c-d866-4b1e-969c-ce4b44630eff"
msgid "Supported Dragn in the quarrel with his brother."
msgstr "형제와 다투는 Dragn의 편을 들어주었습니다."

msgctxt "0409c1fe-6e02-4757-8af5-c45908c76298"
msgid "\\\"I agree with you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 말에 동의해.\\\""

msgctxt "01b37c63-08e7-42ec-8cbe-a880e40aee56"
msgid "\\\"Your brother is dead. Here's your armor.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 형제는 죽었다. 네 갑옷은 여기 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "f7e347ce-a487-4ade-a54e-54fb7ff57ade"
msgid ""
"\\\"Greetings! As you see, I've already set up shop! Took a lot of work, of "
"course, but now I've got a nice place – no worse than the guild's smithy!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"안녕! 보다시피 가게를 열었어! 할 일이 많았지만 좋은 장소를 얻었지. 길드의 대장"
"간보다 나쁘지 않아!\\\""

msgctxt "4f1d43ae-fbe2-463b-a6b8-63ea3993574b"
msgid "\\\"Greetings! Glad to see you in my shop again. How can I serve you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"안녕! 내 가게에 다시 와주어 기쁘군. 무엇이 필요하지?\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "b82343a1-6df9-4781-a331-ec93a3cdba62"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn puffs out his chest and lifts up his chin.{/n} \\\"Well that's rather "
"unfair! So what if I frowned on him traveling to foreign lands? What good did it "
"bring him, anyway? He's got no family, no hearth, no name! He could have been an "
"honest master craftsman, but instead he frittered everything away! Why didn't I "
"want to let him throw his life away? Because I cared.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 고개를 치켜들고 자신만만해 합니다.{/n} \\\"그건 불공평하군! 외국으로 여"
"행가는 그를 내가 싫어하면 어쩌지? 그에게 무슨 좋은 일이 생긴 거야? 그는 가족도 명성"
"도 없어! 정직한 대장장이가 되었을 수도 있지만 그러지 못했지! 그의 삶이 망가지기를 "
"내가 왜 원하겠어? 나도 그를 걱정하는데.\\\""

msgctxt "f7bd31c5-4c03-49fc-be68-8950ec447967"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn grunts and looks at you with distrust.{/n} \\\"So that's how it is... I'm "
"a tyrant, eh? My brother's quite the talker if he's managed to persuade you, of "
"all people. I thought you would understand. You know the burden of responsibility. "
"For the people, for the land. But you're falling for this! A tyrant! I'm an honest "
"craftsman! He's a rascal, a vagabond, and a thief! Decide for yourself if he "
"should have listened to me or not. I'll leave if that's what you want. Thanks for "
"the hospitality. Fare thee well.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 불평하고는 못 믿겠다는 듯 당신을 봅니다.{/n} \\\"그래서 그렇게 된 것이"
"군... 내가 반역자라고? 내 형제 녀석이 너에게 무슨 말을 했는지 모르겠군. 아마 네가 "
"오해를 한 것 같다. 책임감의 무게를 너도 잘 알 거야. 하지만 너는 잘못하고 있어! 반역"
"자라고! 나는 정직한 대장장이일 뿐이야! 그 녀석은 방랑자에 도둑이라고! 그가 내 얘기"
"를 잘 들었어야 했는데. 네가 원하는 대로 하라고. 찾아주어 고맙군.\\\""

msgctxt "83d3babd-ef61-48b0-b268-09dd993cc9c2"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn calms down slowly.{/n} \\\"Is that so? I was trying to set him straight! "
"What a thankless wretch. He betrayed me. How can you trust anyone at all when your "
"own brother is playing dirty tricks on you?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 천천히 진정합니다.{/n} \\\"그래. 그렇단 말이지? 나는 그를 올바른 길로 가"
"게 하려던 것 뿐이야! 정말 배은망덕한 녀석이군. 나를 배신하다니. 형제가 내게 더러운 "
"짓을 하는데 어떻게 다른 사람을 믿겠어?\\\""

msgctxt "2b618d7d-bc36-4c98-9991-8275809be37f"
msgid ""
"\\\"I have no idea. The thieves must have found out what treasure I kept in my "
"workshop, and now it's been stolen. Haven't even had the time to finish the job. "
"Fools! Speaking of which, have you visited the {g|Thorn River}Thorn River{/g} yet? "
"What if the armor is still there? Do you think they've had a chance to pawn it off "
"yet?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"모르겠어. 도둑들이 내 가게에 둔 보물을 찾아서 가져갔을 거야. 하지만 제대로 일"
"을 하지는 못 했겠지. 멍청이들. 그런데 {g|Thorn River}Thorn River{/g}는 방문해 봤"
"어? 갑옷이 아직 거기에 있으면 어쩌지? 그들이 전당포에 넘겨버렸을 거라고 생각해?\\\""

msgctxt "418e84a9-1683-4d26-b24d-49780d8079cf"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn smiles happily, but freezes as he sees the armor.{/n} \\\"Oh damn... "
"Kergan, you scoundrel! Ruining perfectly good armor! I gather he couldn't find a "
"buyer for the whole thing, so he decided to sell it off piece by piece! Ugh, "
"that'll be a lot of repairs! It'll take forever!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 행복하게 웃지만 갑옷을 보자 얼어붙습니다.{/n} \\\"오. 젠장... Kergan. "
"이 나쁜 녀석! 내 갑옷을 망가뜨렸어! 살 사람을 찾지 못해서 조각내어 팔려고 했구나! "
"이런. 고칠 부분이 너무 많아! 시간이 많이 걸리겠어!\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "4202fa1f-d2ea-485a-b13e-d883eb7b0173"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn's face clouds over.{/n} \\\"Here's the story. Our family used to have a "
"suit of plate armor named Lawbringer. My grandfather wore it to perform many "
"heroic deeds. What a great dwarf he was! But it's been stolen. – By my own brother "
"Kergan! And then Kergan fled. Lawbringer has been on my mind ever since. I'd "
"intended to bring the relic back to the clan and restore my good name.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn의 얼굴에 그림자가 드리워집니다.{/n} \\\"이야기 하나 해주지. 우리 가족은 "
"Lawbringer라는 이름의 판갑옷을 가지고 있었어. 내 할아버지가 이것을 입고 업적을 이루"
"셨지. 정말 그는 대단한 드워프였어! 하지만 갑옷이 도둑을 맞았지. 내 형제 Kergan에게 "
"말이야! 그리고 그 녀석은 도망을 쳤어. Lawbringer은 내 마음 속에서 떠나지 않았지. 나"
"는 유물을 클랜에 되돌려주고 명성을 회복하고 싶었어.\\\""

msgctxt "0a58f2c9-23f4-4bd9-a193-a14232a6beb6"
msgid ""
"\\\"It turns out, three local merchants have the three parts of the armor. They're "
"like vultures pulling apart a corpse... They buy whatever catches their eye, not "
"caring whether it's stolen or not. One merchant seems to be in the capital. "
"Another was staying at some trading post. It's got an owner with a strange name... "
"The third one always prowls in distant corners, looking to buy valuables on the "
"cheap. I believe he has an acquaintance – Huntress Dumra. She might well have it.\\"
"\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"시골 상인 세명이 갑옷을 셋으로 나누어 가졌다는군. 시체를 쪼아먹는 독수리 같으"
"니... 훔친 것이든 아니든 그들은 눈에 보이는 것마다 사고는 하지. 상인 하나가 수도에 "
"있는 모양이야. 다른 녀석은 어떤 교역소에 머물렀다고 하고. 정말 이상한 이름의 소유자"
"였어... 세 번째 녀석은 비싼 물건을 싸게 사러 구석진 곳을 돌아다니는 녀석이야. 그는 "
"사냥꾼 Dumra와 아는 사이일 거라고 생각해. 그녀가 그것을 가지고 있을 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "09a1e0b5-11ad-4d64-979c-b20cbb156ed8"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn's cheeks turn beet red, and he says softly,{/n} \\\"Why, it's an honor to "
"indulge your interest. What would you care to know?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn의 뺨은 붉어지고는 당신에게 부드럽게 말합니다.{/n} \\\"정말 영광이군. 무엇"
"을 알고 싶지?\\\""

msgctxt "7cc9a1d5-fdc3-4be2-85ec-7b85f8748a97"
msgid "{n}The dwarf nods gravely.{/n} \\\"Of course.\\\""
msgstr "{n}드워프는 고개를 끄덕입니다.{/n} \\\"물론.\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "ee27ea2c-e29c-487e-aed1-beec649bb9f6"
msgid ""
"\\\"Woradash is a decent, respectable clan. We're considered especially honored, "
"standing out even from among the other clan families. My grandfather accomplished "
"many feats in his time, and my father won respect and honor in many battles. I'm "
"trying hard to be worthy of this legacy. Especially since I'm carrying the load "
"for two.\\\" {n}Dragn's face turns grim.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"Woradash는 존경 받는 클랜이야. 우리는 다른 가문들보다 명예롭다고 생각하지. 우"
"리 할아버지는 많은 업적을 이루었고 우리 아버지는 많은 전투에서 존경을 받았어. 나도 "
"이 유산에 자격이 있으려 노력을 많이 하고 있지. 특히 이 짐을 가지고 온 후로는 더욱."
"\\\" {n}Dragn의 얼굴은 어두워집니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "9fee1dc4-d131-40f0-bce0-eb162593eef0"
msgid ""
"\\\"Our people are masters of making armor and weapons, everyone knows that. We "
"can equip a fighter so that he can fight for hours without getting tired or "
"suffering any wounds. Many have tried to copy our designs and methods, but they're "
"just imitators who don't understand the intricacies of the craft.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"우리는 갑옷과 무기를 만드는 장인이지. 모두 알고 있어. 우리의 갑옷을 입은 전사"
"가 싸우는 도중 상처를 입거나 지치는 경우는 없지. 많은 자들이 우리 작품을 복제하려"
"고 했지만 재능을 따라하기만 해서 싸구려를 만들 뿐이었지.\\\""

msgctxt "e3437c02-2dc2-4917-a2fd-905adcc2921a"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn's face grows grim.{/n} \\\"That's a bad story. My clan has always been "
"proud of its strong blood. My grandfather was a legend, my father was a worthy "
"master, and I, I dare to hope, haven't failed my family. But my brother, Kergan – "
"he's always been a scallywag. Always running off somewhere, looking for trouble... "
"Soon after he came of age he did something terrible. – He stole a clan relic, the "
"armor of my respected grandfather, and took off!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragnd의 얼굴이 어두워집니다.{/n} \\\"그것 참 안 됐군. 우리 클랜은 항상 자존심"
"이 강했는데. 우리 할아버지는 전설이었고 우리 아버지는 뛰어난 장인이었고 나도 그렇"
"게 되고 싶어. 하지만 내 형제 Kergan은 항상 골칫거리지. 항상 도망치고 사고를 치"
"고... 성인이 되고 얼마 안 가서 사고를 치더군. 클랜의 보물인 할아버지의 갑옷을 가져"
"갔던 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "a9ea1860-97d4-41e2-af22-e084f59d3038"
msgid ""
"\\\"Thank you! Oh, thank you! For the armor – and for fixing my brother's head. No "
"one else could do it. It's all right, he can stay in prison for a while. It'll "
"give him time to think, and then I'll bail him out and put him to work. Labor will "
"turn the wretch into a man. I have a major armor-repair job ahead! I came up with "
"some new features for it, but I can't let the secrets slip yet!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"고마워! 오. 고마워! 갑옷을 가져다 줘서 그리고 내 형제의 버릇을 고쳐주어 고마"
"워. 이런 일은 누구도 하지 못 했을 거야. 그는 한동안 감옥에 머물러야 할 거야. 그에"
"게 생각할 시간을 주고 감옥에서 꺼내어 일을 시켜야겠어. 노동은 쓰레기를 인간으로 만"
"들지. 나는 갑옷을 당장 고쳐야 해! 갑옷을 위한 새로운 디자인을 떠올렸지만 아직은 말"
"해줄 수 없어!\\\""

msgctxt "6c8b92f2-ec22-4054-a248-21f4a3c7621e"
msgid ""
"\\\"It was a disgrace. Everyone looked at me like I was the bad seed – because I "
"was the brother of the one who laughed at tradition and desecrated the glory of "
"our family! Eventually I decided I'd had enough. I packed up my things and left "
"the house, looking for a new place – where people wouldn't always be looking at me "
"and whispering. That's how I ended up here.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"참 안 됐군. 내 형제 하나가 전통을 무시하고 우리 가족의 명예를 더럽혀서 모두 나"
"를 불량한 놈으로 보고 있어! 나는 이제 그만해야겠다고 생각했어. 나는 짐을 챙기고 집"
"을 떠나 새로운 곳으로 떠날 거야. 다른 사람들이 나를 보고 흉을 보지 않는 곳으로.\\\""

msgctxt "536758c4-47b6-4cef-98f8-6f552e2b21e7"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn looks discontented, stroking his beard.{/n} \\\"Well, what can I say... "
"There's quite a lot of troublemakers here. And the ones who get called honorable, "
"aren't exemplary law-abiding citizens. I guess it's what lands like these do to "
"people.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 불만스러운 듯 수염을 쓰다듬습니다.{/n} \\\"음. 내가 말할 수 있는 건... "
"여기에 사고뭉치가 많다는 거야. 그 녀석들은 법을 지키지 않는 녀석들이지. 아마 이 땅"
"에 지내서 그런 것 같아.\\\""

msgctxt "94436ae7-d1ba-4ed7-ae84-cb4242812b76"
msgid ""
"\\\"After you hired me, one merchant told me he saw some fragments of armor that "
"looked like Lawbringer. Kergan is such a fool! He couldn't find a buyer for the "
"whole suit – it's too valuable. So he pawned it off piece by piece. Someone got "
"the jambarts, another got the gauntlets, a third got the cuirass. A fine set of "
"armor turned into a pile of junk... fancy junk. See if you can find my "
"grandfather's armor, and bring it back. I promise I will repay you!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"내가 고용되고 나서 법집행자처럼 보이는 갑옷 조각을 보았다고 한 상인이 말하더"
"군. 커간은 멍청한 녀석이야! 이 갑옷이 너무 비싸서 나눠서 팔아야 했던 거야. 전당포"
"에 가서 조금씩 팔았던 거지. 누군가는 몸통을 가지고 있고 누군가는 건틀렛을 다른 누군"
"가는 바지 부분을 가지고 있을 거야. 갑옷 한벌이 쓰레기 더미로 바뀌어버리다니... 화려"
"한 쓰레기로 말이지. 내 할아버지의 갑옷을 본다면 가져다 줘. 반드시 보상해주겠어!\\\""

msgctxt "0cf7f03c-97e3-43b8-b804-6c6657f449c9"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn's face turns scarlet.{/n} \\\"You saw him? And you let him go?! Did you "
"believe his slanderous lies about me torturing him? I was teaching him! – Caring "
"for him! You see, he thought he'd be a hero. Now he's nothing but a poor beggar, a "
"traitor, a disgrace to his name! Stealing from the family! Twice! So, you set him "
"free. I trusted you. I thought you would keep your promise. Ah, to hell with it! "
"I'm not touching a hammer again in my life!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn의 얼굴은 붉어집니다.{/n} \\\"봤어? 그를 그냥 보내주었다고?! 내가 그녀석을 "
"고문했다는 속임수를 믿었던 거야? 나는 그 녀석을 오히려 가르쳤어! 돌봐주고 말이야! "
"자신이 영웅이라고 생각하나 본데 그 녀석은 거지에 반역자에 자기 이름을 더럽힌 놈일 "
"뿐이야! 클랜의 물건을 두번이나 훔치고! 그런데 너는 그를 풀어주었다고. 나는 너를 믿"
"었어. 약속을 지켜줄 거라고 생각했는데. 제길! 다시는 망치를 잡지 않을 거야!\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "79fb9a6e-a8be-4313-9291-982f52c19673"
msgid ""
"\\\"I'm glad you understand. It's all freedom and liberty, and only the likes of "
"you and I are left to safeguard order, and the future. I'm telling you, there will "
"be talks about honesty later! As if they ever worried about honesty while stealing "
"from the decent folk!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"이해해주어 고맙군. 장담하는데 정직에 대한 보상이 언젠가는 생길 거야! 죄 없는 사"
"람의 물건을 훔치고선 정직한 듯 걱정하는군!\\\""

msgctxt "227a5f06-9356-4085-b2e9-40a1e2b19be1"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn takes his eyes from the armor and looks up at you, overwhelmed.{/n} \\"
"\"Dead? Is he? Oh, I knew this would end badly... I knew it, and I didn't do a "
"thing to prevent it.\\\" {n}Dragn grabs the armor and inspects it with a look of "
"indifference.{/n} \\\"So, that's how it is. Perished for nothing, for a piece of "
"iron...\\\" {n}Dwarf stays silent for a few seconds and sighs.{/n} \\\"Thanks for "
"bringing it back all the same. It's just that... I don't think I ought to restore "
"the armor. It's brought such bad luck to the family.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 갑옷을 보다 당신을 올려다 봅니다.{/n} \\\"죽었다고? 그가? 오. 결국 이렇"
"게 될 줄 알았어... 하지만 나는 아무것도 하지 않았구나.\\\" {n}Dragn은 갑옷을 쥐고"
"는 흠이 없나 봅니다.{/n} \\\"그렇게 된 것이군. 헛되이 쇳조각 때문에 죽다니...\\"
"\" {n}드워프는 말 없이 침묵하다가 한숨을 쉽니다.{/n} \\\"되돌려주어 고마워. 그"
"건... 나는 갑옷을 복구할 거라고 생각도 못했어. 이 갑옷이 가족들에게 불운을 안겨주는"
"군.\\\""

msgctxt "0ad41869-a655-4db7-8fc5-1d7d883d1637"
msgid ""
"\\\"Thank you very much for the armor! I hope the thieves got what they deserved. "
"That'll teach them to steal from honest people. Now it's time I get down to work. "
"I have a major armor-repair job ahead! I came up with some new features for it, "
"but I can't let the secrets slip yet!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"갑옷을 되찾아주어 고맙구만! 그 도둑들은 죗값을 치루길 바라. 도둑질을 하면 어떻"
"게 되는지 배워야지. 이제 가서 일할 시간이군. 이제 갑옷을 고쳐야 해! 새로운 갑옷의 "
"모습을 생각해두었지만 아직은 어떻게 생겼는지 말해주지 않겠어!\\\""

msgctxt "3f09cde4-b5b2-44ca-8ebe-804c8fe23ba1"
msgid "Glorious armor that once belonged to a great dwarven hero."
msgstr "한 때 위대한 드워프 영웅이 입던 화려한 갑옷입니다."

msgctxt "99081c2f-93f7-413b-a2fb-06c8e96fa2f2"
msgid "Lawbringer"
msgstr "법집행자"

msgctxt "ab9eee3a-9684-4317-9fbc-1eaf640c7410"
msgid "Gauntlets, formerly part of the Lawbringer armor."
msgstr "갑옷 법집행자의 일부였던 건틀렛입니다."

msgctxt "907d58d8-d65a-4bc4-8829-3b689c0507c5"
msgid "Lawbringer Gauntlets"
msgstr "법집행자 건틀렛"

msgctxt "2d6a7cbc-f76b-4ea8-a1ee-fdbd8b1e4beb"
msgid "A cuirass, formerly part of the Lawbringer armor."
msgstr "갑옷 법집행자의 일부였던 흉갑입니다."

msgctxt "897efdc8-c2b3-430b-a30a-a1e14c21ee9c"
msgid "Lawbringer Cuirass"
msgstr "법집행자의 흉갑"

msgctxt "80e5eec0-fd58-4d2d-b6ea-37ffc492acbb"
msgid "Jambarts, formerly part of the Lawbringer armor."
msgstr "갑옷 법집행자의 일부였던 갑옷 바지입니다."

msgctxt "43fe19d2-0755-4267-b9a0-071d37150133"
msgid "Lawbringer Jambarts"
msgstr "법집행자 갑옷 바지"

msgctxt "06f914ed-cdba-4ca5-96fa-ade4bb1ca2bd"
msgid ""
"A glorious set of armor, which once belonged to a great dwarven hero, and was "
"later disassembled by his descendant."
msgstr ""
"한 때 위대한 드워프 영웅이 입던 화려한 갑옷 세트였지만 한 후손이 조각내었던 물건입"
"니다."

msgctxt "03ec4d91-816b-476d-80e8-fa94db793f4b"
msgid "Incomplete Lawbringer Armor"
msgstr "불완전한 법집행자 갑옷"

msgctxt "acbc0f67-d69b-457d-9ac1-df21d0360020"
msgid "Agreed to pay compensation to Dragn the dwarf."
msgstr "드워프 드렉에게 보상해주기로 약속했습니다."

msgctxt "ee0b5150-99c9-4dbe-a7c9-3fe5298883a5"
msgid "\\\"Fine, I will do as you ask.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"좋아. 요청한 대로 하지.\\\""

msgctxt "b97bc27c-4760-4232-b9e9-c51e35f3b838"
msgid "Ordered Dragn the dwarf to be executed for his bold attitude."
msgstr "무례한 태도를 보인 Dragn에게 처형을 명령했습니다."

msgctxt "ff677617-53f4-4283-a450-e9ff373cf78e"
msgid "\\\"You think you can demand something from me? Hang him.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나에게서 무얼 바란다고? 저 놈을 교수대에 보내라.\\\""

msgctxt "2ba41038-eabc-4cb1-8740-7e10629aba7f"
msgid "\\\"You get nothing from me. Leave at once.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나에게서 뺏을 수는 없어. 꺼져.\\\""

msgctxt "eb1c4b84-31fd-491a-8e14-a006c1fed020"
msgid "\\\"Thank you for your gift.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 재능이 정말 도움이 되는군.\\\""

msgctxt "828f2e66-6979-41c0-b996-65f1cf458bb9"
msgid "\\\"I need something from you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에게서 원하는 것이 있다.\\\""

msgctxt "05faccd5-f848-452b-8175-fdcf77fa68e2"
msgid "\\\"Leave my lands.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내 땅을 떠나라.\\\""

msgctxt "97bf57bf-a25d-49be-8867-1bf9c93ed818"
msgid ""
"\\\"Put everything else aside and get to repairing your grandfather's armor!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"하던 일은 그만두고 네 할아버지의 갑옷을 고쳐!\\\""

msgctxt "77ba1827-32cf-4f86-8465-b86a502dff9b"
msgid "\\\"I think you know best what to make.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"무얼 만들어야 할지 잘 알고 있겠지.\\\""

msgctxt "8c0e0594-2f08-4015-a27b-db24a22914d4"
msgid "\\\"A one-handed hammer.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"한손 망치.\\\""

msgctxt "5e39af15-01d8-458c-8fc9-2cfcfd3859e8"
msgid "\\\"A one-handed axe.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"한손 도끼.\\\""

msgctxt "110e8bae-962e-4cda-898d-b7b4268fa465"
msgid "\\\"A crossbow.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"석궁.\\\""

msgctxt "d589fc57-25bb-4801-8710-926daaf711a3"
msgid "\\\"A metal shield.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"쇠방패.\\\""

msgctxt "9677c228-be23-4bbb-9d60-d3414601ee2c"
msgid "\\\"Plate armor.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"판갑옷.\\\""

msgctxt "a285fa89-4268-4198-b6e5-0d371ec16091"
msgid "\\\"Make something in the dwarvish style.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"드워프 스타일로 만들어줘.\\\""

msgctxt "d095c7f6-a721-494e-a881-4dd19f5d0fcc"
msgid "Got rid of Dragn the dwarf with using bureaucratic procrastination."
msgstr "게으름을 부리는 Dragn을 제거했습니다."

msgctxt "d453a431-9eb2-4646-ba93-da6c04378119"
msgid ""
"My advisors will check your calculations. To the digit. Unfortunately, they "
"already have a great deal to do as it is, so the gods only know when they'll have "
"time to look at your petition.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"내 조언자들이 네 계산을 확인할 거야. 한자리수까지. 불행히도 그들은 경험이 많아"
"서 너는 곧 빌어야 할지도 몰라.\\\""

msgctxt "4e478d55-3a42-45c0-bca7-555514e0ef57"
msgid ""
"{n}A young dwarf in worn-out clothes shows you a scroll of fine paper with an "
"expensive seal. He speaks ceremoniously, like a herald.{/n} \\\"Greetings. My name "
"is Dragn Woradash. I come to you, {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your "
"Highness} with a request. Or to be precise, to receive compensation.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}닳은 옷을 입은 어린 드워프가 당신에게 비싼 봉인이 되어있는 고급 종이 스크롤을 보"
"입니다. 그는 점잔게 말합니다.{/n} \\\"안녕하신가. 나는 Woradash의 Dragn. 요청을 받"
"고 여기로 왔지. 정확시는 보상을 받으러 왔어.\\\""

msgctxt "39cb295e-9d18-4bf6-8849-80292f167949"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf blinks several times, surprised.{/n} \\\"You agree? Just like... like "
"that? Seriously... I never thought I'd meet, in this land of thieves, a ruler who "
"so honored the law. You are a truly a worthy ruler. Well, then, I guess we'll meet "
"when you satisfy my petition. My respects!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프는 눈을 깜빡입니다.{/n} \\\"정말이야? 그렇게 쉽게...? 참... 이 도둑들이 넘"
"치는 땅에서 지배자를 만날 줄이야. 너는 정말 놀라운 지배자야. 내 부탁을 들어주었을 "
"때 다시 보면 좋겠군. 그럼 이만!\\\""

msgctxt "ec1db9ee-2543-4695-a9af-8a0728f20cea"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf's face twists in a mix of fear and anger.{/n} \\\"For pity's sake, "
"for what?! This is lawlessness! Outrage!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프의 얼굴은 공포와 분노로 일그러집니다.{/n} \\\"정말 딱하군. 무법지대나 다"
"름 없어! 젠장!\\\""

msgctxt "3996a46b-8e42-4fa9-b68a-37955e258397"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf sniffs.{/n} \\\"I knew I was never going to find justice here. "
"There's nothing but thieves and robbers around these parts. If you're not holding "
"on to it tightly enough, it's as good as gone!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프가 코웃음을 칩니다.{/n} \\\"여기서 정의를 찾을 수는 없을 거라 생각했어. "
"이 곳에는 도둑들이 넘쳐나는군. 약속을 지키지 않는다면 영원히 사라질 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "071657a2-ca83-4db5-b45e-8b209ba5f6bc"
msgid ""
"{n}{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d} bows, coughing quietly into his beard.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your "
"Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, I would like to apologize. I "
"suppose I was a little... headstrong during my last visit. I have a bad temper. In "
"the mountains they used to call me Grumbler. Well, I didn't expect my petition to "
"be taken seriously. No one wants to share with strangers, even if their demands "
"are quite lawful. Please know that I appreciate your honesty.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d}은 인사를 하고는 점잖게 기침을 합니다.{/n} \\\"사과를 하고 싶"
"군. 내가 조금... 저번에는 무례했지. 기분이 좋질 않았어. 산에서 나는 불평쟁이라고 불"
"리고는 했지. 내 부탁이 그렇게 진지하게 들리지 않았나보군. 찾는 사람이 있더라도 이방"
"인과 나누고 싶지는 않아. 정직한 건 감사하구만.\\\""

msgctxt "c10e5117-cfd6-4b59-8874-27bf42257264"
msgid ""
"{n}{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d} bows from the waist and addresses you ceremoniously.{/n} \\"
"\"Greetings, {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}. By tradition, "
"if a worthy ruler is patron to a master, the master gives generously in return. I "
"have come to honor this tradition.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d}은 인사를 하고는 예의 바르게 말을 겁니다.{/n} \\\"안녕한가! 전"
"통에 따라 지배자가 장인을 방문하면 장인은 인사하는 게 예의지. 나는 전통을 지키는 드"
"워프야.\\\""

msgctxt "f187ffb8-70b4-4a4b-bc3a-13702ce93620"
msgid "\\\"Please accept this. I worked hard on it. I hope it serves you well.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"부디 이걸 받아줘. 나는 열심히 일했다고. 너는 받을 자격이 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "243f99d3-a230-4682-bec2-c9fad7e7297f"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn solemnly presents the reforged plate armor.{/n} \\\"Here, {mf|Your Grace|"
"Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}. The work is complete. Grandfather's armor "
"is restored. It has belonged to the family for many years, but my family is no "
"more... So I present it to you.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 고쳐진 판갑옷을 보여줍니다.{/n} \\\"여기. 가져가게. 작업이 끝났어. 할아"
"버지의 갑옷이 고쳐졌지. 이것은 오랫동안 클랜의 것이었지만 우리 가족은 더 이상 존재"
"하지 않아... 그러니 선물로 주는 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "a6d77b69-c88a-43c4-ad59-44048f8c5d22"
msgid "\\\"A master always welcomes a good customer! So what would you like?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"장인은 항상 손님을 반기지! 그래서 무얼 원하지?\\\""

msgctxt "a68fd211-c614-4403-997a-6903104d3250"
msgid ""
"\\\"It is a decent piece of work, to be fair, but not a masterpiece. Masterpieces "
"are rare, once-in-a-lifetime accomplishments. Anyway, I have an idea how to use "
"our family relic for your greater glory... but I'm going to need your help. Come "
"by if you're interested. I'll tell you more.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"이것은 뛰어난 작품이지만 걸작은 아니야. 걸작은 희귀하고 인생에 걸쳐 한번 나올"
"까 말까하는 것이지. 어쨌든 우리 클랜의 보물을 잘 사용하는 방법을 생각해 두었지... "
"하지만 네 도움이 먼저 필요해. 흥미가 있다면 방문해줘. 그 때 더 설명하지.\\\""

msgctxt "a108820f-7049-45e8-a84a-0ae7334daeaf"
msgid ""
"\\\"If my gift pleases you, please respond in kind. I've been robbed. Some thieves "
"crept into my workshop and took all my gold, and Lawbringer too! I hadn't even had "
"a chance to finish it! The people are saying that robbers, thieves, and murderers "
"have lately been freely roaming the area. They gather along the {g|Thorn River}"
"Thorn River{/g}, near the ford. You're the ruler, so please, I beg you, take "
"action to find it!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"내 재능이 마음에 든다면 나를 도와줘. 나는 도둑 맞았어. 어떤 도둑이 기어들어와 "
"내 금과 법집행자 갑옷을 가져갔어! 아직 마무리도 짓지 못했는데! 사람들이 그러는데 도"
"둑과 살인자가 돌아다닌다고 하더군. 그들은 {g|Thorn River}Thorn River{/g} 주위를 서"
"성인다고 해. 너는 지배자니 부디 내 물건을 찾아줘!\\\""

msgctxt "4e18c965-e9fd-4e37-9a3d-4e440c2e07ab"
msgid ""
"\\\"If you have any requests or needs, feel free to tell me. Otherwise, please "
"allow me to devote my time to Lawbringer. I'm itching to finish what I've begun, "
"and restore my grandfather's heritage.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"필요한 게 있다면 언제든지 말해줘. 그렇지 않다면 나는 법집행자를 완성하겠어. 시"
"작한 것을 어서 끝내고 싶어. 우리 할아버지의 유산을.\\\""

msgctxt "ef211d18-7e3e-4d8a-b175-dded71419afd"
msgid ""
"\\\"Gladly! I've been itching to start! But a craftsman's word is law. No new work "
"until I complete all my current orders. I'm not some ordinary fool whose mind is "
"so full of fantasies and \\\"fresh ideas\\\" that he can't properly finish a "
"single task!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"기꺼이! 어서 시작하고 싶었어! 하지만 장인의 말이 곧 법이지. 내 명령이 끝날 때까"
"지 새로운 일의 시작은 없어. 나는 공상에 빠진 멍청이가 아니니까. 내가 한 일은 끝을 "
"맺지!\\\""

msgctxt "40abe279-0178-4937-8042-0064e68631a5"
msgid "\\\"It's a pleasure to work hard for such an honorable {mf|lord|lady}.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이렇게 일을 하게 되어 정말 영광이군.\\\""

msgctxt "cea000b4-00ac-44bf-adec-3043bb1acb24"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn points his chin upwards, insulted.{/n} \\\"This is your land, you're free "
"to throw me out. I'll always be happy to leave a place where honest citizens are "
"unwelcome!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn은 턱을 들며 말합니다.{/n} \\\"이곳은 네 땅이고 나를 나가라고 하는 것은 네 "
"마음이지. 정직한 시민이 환영받지 못하는 곳이라면 나는 기꺼이 나가겠어!\\\""

msgctxt "98ca1126-58e1-42f2-918c-45cbefc2ef9e"
msgid ""
"{n}Dragn nods pensively.{/n} \\\"Of course... My kind are rarely allowed to work "
"freely, without a big hurry...\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Dragn이 고개를 끄덕입니다.{/n} \\\"물론... 서두르지 않고 일을 하면 좋지...\\\""

msgctxt "386ff4d6-fcfb-4b5e-8afc-72dc015790c2"
msgid ""
"\\\"Will do. It will be heavy enough to split open a suit of armor, but light "
"enough that you won't get tired of holding it.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그래. 갑옷 한벌을 쪼개는 것은 힘든 일이지만 입고 있을 때는 충분히 가벼울 거야."
"\\\""

msgctxt "bf9951fa-ac2b-44ee-bdfb-dd6a9a900ad2"
msgid ""
"\\\"Most reasonable. Nowadays they don't even think it's a real victory unless you "
"overpower them hand to hand. But if you ask me, shooting bolts from a distance is "
"smarter than getting bludgeoned to death. Let the fools think what they like, but "
"you and I – we know better.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그렇군. 그들에게 힘을 행사하지 않는다면 그것이 진정한 승리라고 생각하지 않을 거"
"야. 나에게 묻는다면 먼 거리에서 쏘는 것이 가까이서 싸우다 죽는 것보다 낫지. 바보들"
"은 그냥 두어. 우리가 더 똑똑하니.\\\""

msgctxt "c60c075d-f5f3-49b2-ae43-649906ee4277"
msgid ""
"\\\"Very wise. One should never forget about protection. Everyone thinks of glory "
"and victory – a sharper axe, a heavier hammer. Never stop to think about their "
"bones. Ha ha! The fools!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"현명하군. 보호는 항상 신경 써야 하지. 모두 영광과 승리를 원하지. 날카로운 도끼"
"와 무거운 망치 같은 것도. 하지만 자기들이 약골이라는 생각은 안 해! 바보들!\\\""

msgctxt "8f905469-65ba-4e72-acd8-08cbcae14f5b"
msgid ""
"\\\"I see you're a true expert. No one has ever achieved greater success in "
"smithing than my people.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"네가 전문가인건 알겠어. 우리 보다 대장장이 실력이 뛰어난 자들은 없지.\\\""

msgctxt "9f777ecb-2cce-4db7-a156-cac698191ae7"
msgid ""
"\\\"Here, take a look. This scroll contains a list of expenses for building the {g|"
"Road of Shields}Road of Shields{/g}. The cost of laying the stone, draining, "
"cutting firebreaks and so on. You and your people have lived for a long time on "
"lands that lawfully belonged to my people, making free use of the fruits of "
"someone else's labor. Would you now please pay for the work my ancestors did?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"여기 보라고. 이 스크롤은 {g|Road of Shields}Road of Shields{/g}를 짓는 데 들어"
"간 비용이 적혀있어. 돌을 놓고 물을 대고 나무를 구하는 등의 비용 말이지. 너희 사람들"
"은 우리의 땅에서 오래 살면서 남의 재산을 마음대로 썼지. 이제 와서 보상을 하고 싶다"
"는 건가?\\\""

msgctxt "76cc1b3d-cfc6-4c41-8abd-63c020768e3d"
msgid ""
"\\\"I, Dragn Woradash, humbly demand compensation for those who are no longer able "
"to collect. I do not ask for gold. It's better that you give me a house with a "
"shop, which will costs as much as the sum in the scroll. You see, I'm a "
"blacksmith, and I'm used to earning my living honestly – but I can't work without "
"a shop. As soon as I get what's mine, I'll open the shop right away. Then you'll "
"have at least one decent bladesmith.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"나 Dragn Woradash. 더 이상 수집할 수 없는 자에게 보상을 요구하겠어. 나는 금을 "
"원하는 것이 아니야. 가게가 딸린 집을 줘. 이 스크롤에 적인 동일한 금액의 집을. 나는 "
"대장장이이니 내 일을 하며 살고 싶지만 가게 없이 일할 수는 없지. 가게가 생기면 곧 장"
"사를 시작할 거야. 그렇다면 너도 대장장이 하나가 생기고 좋은 것이지.\\\""

msgctxt "eef61d62-e4f7-4e32-96d5-dc73ad5e4aa7"
msgid ""
"\\\"{g|Road of Shields}The Road of Shields{/g} used to run through your lands. It "
"was built, among others, by my ancestors, members of the noble Woradash clan. This "
"means they still own it, even though they were driven from these lands. According "
"to all law, if a bandit takes my father's house and kills him, the house still "
"belongs to me. So I've come for what's mine.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"{g|Road of Shields}The Road of Shields{/g}는 너희 땅으로 나 있지. 이것은 내 조"
"상인 Woradash 클랜에서 만든 것이야. 그 말은 그들이 소유권을 가지고 있다는 거지. 법"
"에 따르면 도둑이 아버지의 집을 훔치고 그를 죽여도 집은 여전히 아들의 것이라고 해. "
"그러니 나는 내가 원하는 것을 받겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "5e07b20b-0389-4cd2-884b-30b2b5e92a36"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf opens his mouth to say something... then clearly can't find the "
"words. He huffs indignantly, shifts from foot to foot, then finally turns away, "
"defeated.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프는 입을 열어 무언가를 말하려고 하는데... 하지 못합니다. 그는 기침을 하더"
"니 등을 돌리고 걸어갑니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "7d37415c-8def-44b4-89fe-e07b7c9afe94"
msgid ""
"\\\"I adjusted all the parts for a better fit, reworked a thing or two... Here you "
"go. Wear it proudly. It is not by coincidence that it was named Lawbringer. It "
"will aid a just lord in delivering law to {mf|his|her} honest people. It's going "
"to fit you perfectly.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"모든 부위를 손봤지... 여기 있네. 잘 쓰게. 이것이 법집행자라고 불리는 이유는 분"
"명히 있어. 정직한 사람들을 위해 법을 집행하는 지배자를 위한 것이지. 너에게 딱 맞아."
"\\\""

msgctxt "2bbac27b-cc0b-4825-bd39-161b866bbc66"
msgid ""
"\\\"All right, I'll begin working on my grandfather's armor. I've been looking "
"forward to this!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"좋아. 내 할아버지 갑옷을 계속 고치겠어. 어서 끝내고 싶군!\\\""

msgctxt "5d647a09-3a55-4d60-9233-0e163fdde31a"
msgid "\\\"Show me what's in the bag.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"가방에 든 것을 보여줘.\\\""

msgctxt "2d39fb86-1147-483e-9ac0-b9c80f00180b"
msgid "Executed the lawbringer thief without talking."
msgstr "대화를 하지 않고 법집행자 갑옷 도둑을 처형합니다."

msgctxt "d1be4cdf-75d6-41a1-9361-5005606a920b"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"Thieves are executed in these lands.\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"도둑은 이 땅에서 처형 당한다.\\\""

msgctxt "478f658a-03c3-4a78-b08a-8c61f41af4c2"
msgid "Encouraged Kergan to stop escaping the rule of law and confess."
msgstr "도망치지 말고 자백하라고 커간을 설득합니다."

msgctxt "4b2be5c1-b52f-4db9-83a4-60379593f486"
msgid ""
"\\\"You cheated your own brother, sold the family relic... Aren't you ashamed of "
"yourself?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 형을 속이고 클랜의 보물을 팔았지... 부끄럽지도 않은가?\\\""

msgctxt "b1f0794b-d997-4f80-967f-7ca18305f441"
msgid "Arrested Kergan, the lawbringer thief."
msgstr "법집행자 갑옷 도둑 커간을 체포합니다."

msgctxt "a1c25974-b6f5-4280-8188-fcaee5e95e75"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"It's time I teach you a lesson!\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"도덕을 가르쳐 주겠다!\\\""

msgctxt "33a130dc-f887-4b35-acd8-3390e57bc469"
msgid "Let Kergan get away with the armor stolen from his evil elder brother."
msgstr "그의 나쁜 형으로부터 커간이 훔친 갑옷을 가지고 도망치게 둡니다."

msgctxt "9cb4cf5e-9aa4-4c88-a702-8d3524358ed3"
msgid "\\\"You're right. Your brother is a tyrant. Go in peace.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네가 맞아. 네 형은 나쁜 녀석이야. 어서 가라.\\\""

msgctxt "c67df00c-9560-49c0-b356-498d3d744dda"
msgid ""
"\\\"I don't care about your family feud. I just need the armor. Hand it over.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 가족 일은 상관 없어. 나는 갑옷만 있으면 돼. 어서 넘겨.\\\""

msgctxt "7091f7a2-37a8-447b-83fe-09ea6556cc77"
msgid "Put Kergan in jail."
msgstr "커간을 감옥에 집어넣습니다."

msgctxt "79d940bd-ead1-4bde-9f2b-e77cd1503b3d"
msgid ""
"\\\"You'll be going to jail until your trial. After that, I'll let your brother "
"deal with you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"심판이 있을 때까지 감옥에 있어라. 그 후 너는 네 형을 볼 것이다.\\\""

msgctxt "4f2ce098-fd56-4a79-aebd-5545b19200bb"
msgid "Killed Kergan after he'd surrendered."
msgstr "항복한 커간을 죽입니다."

msgctxt "cf5464d9-73b8-47dc-969b-db0b12b87a14"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"Time to rid my country of one more pathetic thief!\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"내 땅에서 도둑 하나를 더 줄일 시간이군.\\\""

msgctxt "4eb13596-d120-4870-9d59-d3bcc313ad75"
msgid "\\\"Who are you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너는 누구지?\\\""

msgctxt "c38015d4-16d0-46b0-9a75-bc2a86440a98"
msgid "Set Kergan free."
msgstr "커간을 풀어줍니다."

msgctxt "acb15b82-7f84-4430-9622-674dc4ef9d0e"
msgid ""
"\\\"I won't tell your brother you stole from him. Now take yourself from my lands "
"and never return.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"네가 형을 도둑질 하지 않았다고 말하지 않겠다. 이제 내 땅에서 꺼지고 다시는 오"
"지 말아라.\\\""

msgctxt "c5e36985-9659-4321-b296-bb6637996e29"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf stashes something hastily in a big bag when he spots you.{/n} \\"
"\"Um... What do you want? I mean, how can I help you?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프는 서둘러 커다란 가방을 정리합니다.{/n} \\\"음... 나 한테 왜그래? 아니... "
"무슨 일로 왔어?\\\""

msgctxt "e8d46fcd-0677-4c0c-8b18-a430d9c9e4bc"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf turns pale.{/n} \\\"{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d} sent you after me? Please "
"don't kill me! I'm Kergan, his younger brother. What stories did he tell you about "
"me? That I stole from him? Well maybe I did. But he's the one who started it! "
"Always bossing me around, saying he was older. Do this, don't do that! He was "
"trying to strangle my talent! I'm an adventurer by nature! Adventure lures me! And "
"he tells me my passion is nothing but prowling and roguery!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프가 창백해집니다.{/n} \\\"{d|Dragn}Dragn{/d}이 너를 보냈다고? 제발 나를 죽"
"이지 말아줘! 나는 그의 동생 커간이라고 해. 그가 무슨 얘기를 했지? 내가 그의 물건을 "
"훔쳤다고? 그랬을 수도 있지. 하지만 그가 먼저 시작했어! 항상 자기가 나이가 많다며 나"
"를 구박했지. 이거 해라, 저거 해라 하면서 말이야. 내 재능은 알아주지도 않았어! 나는 "
"타고난 여행가야! 여행이 나를 유혹하지. 하지만 그는 나를 그저 도둑으로 몰았어!\\\""

msgctxt "5b89d2bf-20a2-405e-a562-da84fc3cd945"
msgid ""
"{n}Kergan flinches as if he's been hit, and then droops.{/n} \\\"You're right. I'm "
"ashamed. I dreamt of returning home with wealth and glory, so Dragn would see how "
"dumb he was. Now I've embarrassed myself, and I can't dare look him in the eye. It "
"turns out I was the fool, not he.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}커간은 맞은 것처럼 몸을 움츠립니다.{/n} \\\"네가 맞아. 부끄럽군. 부와 영광을 가"
"지고 집으로 가겠다고 생각했는데. 드렉이 나를 인정하게 말이야. 이제 나는 부끄럽군. "
"그의 눈을 볼 수도 없어. 내가 바보였어.\\\""

msgctxt "77090797-a6a8-44bd-88dd-75aecd77373b"
msgid ""
"{n}Kergan shrugs.{/n} \\\"Why would I be ashamed? It's my life. I'm not going to "
"live my life just to satisfy my brother. Freedom means a lot to me. I'll make up "
"for today's sins with tomorrow's good deeds.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}커간이 어깨를 으쓱합니다.{/n} \\\"왜 내가 부끄러워 해야 하지? 이건 내 인생이야. "
"나는 내 형을 만족시키려고 사는 게 아니야. 자유는 나에게 많은 것을 의미하지. 나는 오"
"늘의 죄를 내일의 선행으로 갚겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "0718f04b-bfc6-4465-9355-9a942e24e945"
msgid ""
"{n}Kergan wipes the sweat from his forehead.{/n} \\\"It's all right, it's all "
"right. I should go. Tell Dragn I don't care about him, or his advice, or his "
"forges and hammers. I've got my own way.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}커간이 이마에서 땀을 닦습니다.{/n} \\\"좋아. 알겠어. 나는 가야겠어. 드렉에게 나"
"는 신경 쓰지 않는다고 말해줘. 나는 내 갈 길을 가겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "6f9eaac8-885c-452b-bb7e-d7bc9563d35c"
msgid ""
"\\\"Become a master, he said. Work hard in the family forge, he said. I'm sick to "
"death of forges! I know it's a custom, but it's a stupid one. I want to see the "
"world! To perform great feats! There's no adventuring without armor and a sword! "
"So I took grandfather's armor. It was no use gathering dust like a holy relic! I "
"wanted my chance at glory. I wanted it to serve our family honorably one more time!"
"\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"장인이 되라고 그가 말했지. 클랜의 대장간에서 열심히 일하라고. 대장간은 이제 질"
"렸어! 전통이라는 건 알지만 멍청해. 나는 세상을 보고 싶어! 위대한 업적을 이루고 싶다"
"고. 갑옷과 검이 없다면 모험은 없는 것이지. 그래서 할아버지의 갑옷을 가져갔어. 그런 "
"유물을 먼지가 쌓이게 둘 수는 없지! 나는 영광을 얻을 기회를 얻고 싶었어. 내 가족의 "
"이름을 다시 영광스럽게 하고 싶었지!\\\""

msgctxt "736bfb3c-99d2-46b9-8b28-e1d85873adc6"
msgid ""
"\\\"But... the whole hero thing didn't exactly work out. I had to sell the armor "
"to feed myself. I swear, I was going to buy it back... I just needed more time. "
"While I was gathering my strength, I heard there was a blacksmith named Dragn, who "
"was forging some legendary armor. I realized this could be my second chance! I "
"know I already did him an awful wrong – but if he hadn't hounded me so, I would "
"have become a respectful adventurer, a world traveler, and a wealthy man!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"하지만... 모험을 하는 것도 소용이 없었어. 나는 먹고 살기 위해 갑옷을 팔아야 했"
"지. 하지만 돈이 생기면 다시 사려고 했어... 그저 시간이 필요했던 것 뿐이야. 돈을 모"
"으는 동안 나는 드렉이라는 대장장이가 전설의 갑옷을 고치고 있다는 소문을 들었어. 나"
"는 그게 두번째 기회가 될 거라고 생각했지! 그에게 끔찍한 짓을 저지른 건 인정해. 하지"
"만 나를 그렇게 볶지 않았다면 더 존경 받는 모험가이자 부자가 되어있었을 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "50c21f71-3e89-4bfd-b2aa-6a12f226c4cf"
msgid ""
"{n}The dwarf lifts up his hands in despair.{/n} \\\"Oh... all right, all right! "
"Just don't use your fists!\\\" {n}Kergan bites his lip.{/n} \\\"What are you going "
"to do to me?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드워프는 절망스럽게 손을 올립니다.{/n} \\\"오... 좋아! 때리지만 말아줘!\\\" {n}"
"커간은 입술을 깨뭅니다.{/n} \\\"나에게 무슨 짓을 하려는 거야?\\\""

msgctxt "04b899f1-9131-407f-8201-503d5f5c4774"
msgid ""
"\\\"No way! If that's how you're going to behave, then just go ahead and try to "
"take it by force!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"안 돼! 그렇게 할 거라면 그냥 때려서 가져가!\\\""

msgctxt "d570bfc3-0565-4061-8f44-4f9e7567f7a9"
msgid ""
"\\\"Have mercy! Please, don't kill me! I'll give you everything! Here's the armor "
"– take it! Just spare my life!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"부탁이야! 죽이지 말아줘! 뭐든 줄게! 여기 갑옷 가져가! 목숨만 살려줘!\\\""

msgctxt "9e52209a-d555-4779-8927-f84183e28be7"
msgid ""
"\\\"Thank you! Thank you so much! I'll change! Just don't kill me!\\\" {n}The "
"dwarf slumps down onto the ground, exhausted.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"고마워! 정말 고마워! 이제 열심히 살게! 죽이지만 말아줘!\\\" {n}드워프는 바닥에 "
"엎드려 빕니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "91bc121e-c87f-4107-8db7-776310584898"
msgid ""
"\\\"I'm Kerg... Kergabas! Dwarf Kergabas! Just a stranger on my way to, um... {g|"
"Andoran}Andoran{/g}!\\\" {n}Judging from the look on the dwarf's face, the name \\"
"\"Kergabas\\\" sounds just as dumb to him.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"나는 커... 커가바스야! 드워프 커가바스지! 그저 {g|Andoran}Andoran{/g}으로 가는 "
"중이었지!\\\" {n}드워프의 모습으로 판단하건데 커가바스라는 이름은 어색하게 들립니"
"다.{/n}"

msgctxt "e75fbfec-7e27-482e-81ab-cbc216d0d0a4"
msgid ""
"\\\"I know, it's all my fault. I stole from my kin, from my own brother... but "
"don't punish me, I beg you! I can go to jail if you like! Or maybe... maybe you "
"could just set me free? Please don't hurt me!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"내 잘못이야. 내가 형에게서 훔쳤어... 하지만 나를 벌하지는 말아줘! 부탁이야! 감"
"옥에 가라고 하면 갈게! 아니면... 그냥 나를 풀어주면 안 될까? 때리지만 말아줘!\\\""

msgctxt "ed737619-a140-4d83-8664-5218ce7903ab"
msgid ""
"\\\"You know what? You can take the armor. I'll... I'll go to the city and "
"surrender to the guards. I'm tired of running away... There's no point. There's no "
"escaping your own guilt. I'll serve my sentence, and after that I'll lead a "
"different life, a clean one! My brother might even take me back!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그냥 갑옷 가져가. 나는... 도시로 가서 경비에게 자수하겠어. 도망은 질렸어... 다 "
"소용 없어. 도망가도 소용 없어. 나는 심판을 받고 깨끗한 삶을 살겠어! 내 형을 다시 만"
"난다고 해도 말이야!\\\""

msgctxt "348e67c0-d32b-43d2-9c36-4f67fe838e18"
msgid ""
"\\\"Oh, really? Oh, boy! Thank you so much! I'll pay you back in full when I "
"become a great hero!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"오. 정말이야! 오! 정말 고마워! 내가 영웅이 되면 빚을 갚을게!\\\""

msgctxt "ac0a22ff-991a-4b4b-950b-7f70ca314879"
msgid "\\\"I have to go.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나는 가야 해.\\\""

msgctxt "6ddbd49d-a684-4c43-bbd4-85cf28a6005f"
msgid "Killed Sartayne on the spot."
msgstr "그 자리에서 Sartayne을 죽였습니다."

msgctxt "114d7013-b761-4315-be71-e0ca978677a7"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"You shouldn't have interfered with my servants.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9c7e8690-5626-4f9f-8331-8774dee0b116"
msgid "Let Sartayne go to avenge his father."
msgstr "Sartayne이 자신의 아버지를 복수하게 둡니다."

msgctxt "206ee87c-0d0d-4a61-800a-03012a2a4c07"
msgid ""
"\\\"I recognize your right to revenge, and this is your business. But I'm not "
"helping you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 복수는 정당하고 이건 네 일이야. 하지만 너를 돕지는 않겠다.\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "368c652a-463d-4947-8a37-5fc4656848b0"
msgid "Conspired with Nazrielle's enemy and broke your deal with her."
msgstr "Nazrielle의 적과 한 통이 되어 그녀와의 약속을 저버립니다."

msgctxt "b3a3d5a4-1616-4692-8b03-ad949799e907"
msgid "\\\"Deal. You will be my new master.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"좋아. 네가 내 새로운 주인이다.\\\""

msgctxt "444d0dad-00a8-4342-b4dd-3a09b7ded119"
msgid "Honored the deal and protected Nazrielle from Sartayne."
msgstr "Sartayne로부터 Nazrielle을 보호하고 약속을 지키게 합니다."

msgctxt "b3ff6dd6-1028-40bb-8e46-119595f9ea33"
msgid "\\\"I respect our deal with Nazrielle. You're going to jail.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"Nazrielle의 약속도 중요해. 너는 감옥으로 가라.\\\""

msgctxt "65fd9ad5-03cd-4005-b9cf-77ae566186bd"
msgid "\\\"You've been spoiling Nazrielle's work, haven't you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"Nazrielle를 방해했지?\\\""

msgctxt "913034a9-fdb2-41f0-9782-b5d4e8157534"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne gazes at you in astonishment. Something seems different. No longer "
"does he appear dim-witted and servile. Instead he seems self-confident and firm.{/"
"n} \\\"I didn't expect to see you here. How can I help you?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 놀라서 당신을 봅니다. 무언가 이상합니다. 그는 더 이상 멍청해 보이지 "
"않습니다. 그는 오히려 자신감이 넘쳐보입니다.{/n} \\\"너를 여기서 볼 거라고 생각은 "
"못 했어. 필요한 게 있나?\\\""

msgctxt "0bf2e621-7f6c-4acb-9f64-8d6143b922d2"
msgid ""
"\\\"When I found out the rascal was here, I decided to seize the opportunity. I "
"arrived here, got myself an apprentice's position... and set my hands to work. I'm "
"smarter and more skilled than she might think. I worked hard by the anvil during "
"the day and crafted cursed items at nights. Nazrielle's pride is her soft spot – "
"the perfect place to strike. I decided to tarnish her image, make her look clumsy "
"and incompetent, ruin her reputation. And, of course, destroy that masterpiece "
"she's been making such a fuss over...\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그 녀석을 여기에서 봤을 때 나는 기회를 잡으리라고 생각했어. 여기로 도착해서는 "
"도제 일을 하기 시작했지. 나는 그녀가 생각했던 것보다 똑똑하고 재주가 좋았어. 나는 "
"낮에는 모루에서 일하고 밤에는 저주받은 아이템들을 손봤지. 나즈릴르의 약점은 자존심"
"이었어. 나는 그녀의 명성을 더럽히기로 생각하고 그녀의 명성을 망치기로 했지. 그리고 "
"그녀가 노력해서 만든 걸작도 파괴할 거라고 생각했지...\\\""

msgctxt "38fad6ee-1351-49a2-a3b9-fcb869177fac"
msgid ""
"\\\"That's a shame. Now if you'll excuse me, I have to go. If you managed to find "
"me here, Nazrielle will too. Tell the lousy skunk I quit. But she'd better run "
"like hell. I will have my revenge.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"안타깝군. 괜찮다면 나는 가봐야겠어. 나를 찾을 수 있었으니 Nazrielle도 찾을 수 "
"있을 거야. 그 멍청이에게 나는 그만둔다고 전해줘. 그녀는 도망치는 게 좋을 거야. 나"
"는 복수를 할 거니까.\\\""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "2a19ba93-bfe7-4cf7-8854-178556a4b32f"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne's laugh rings out.{/n} \\\"So that's how it is. As soon as I take over "
"Nazrielle's workshop, I promise, I will forge things you've never even dreamed of! "
"And its former owner will receive some proper training, I give you my word. I'll "
"begin by bringing some guards to the blacksmith shop and suppress any thoughts she "
"has of resistance. Goodbye, {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}."
"\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne의 웃음이 퍼집니다.{/n} \\\"그렇게 된 것이군. 나즈릴르의 가게를 물려받으"
"면 네가 꿈꾸지 못했던 아이템을 만들어주겠어! 전 주인은 적절한 훈련을 받아야 할 거"
"야. So that's how it is. As soon as I take over Nazrielle's workshop, I promise, I "
"will forge things you've never even dreamed of! And its former owner will receive "
"some proper training, I give you my word. I'll begin by bringing some guards to "
"the blacksmith shop and suppress any thoughts she has of resistance. Goodbye, {mf|"
"Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}.\\\""

msgctxt "434bd7a5-ea00-42a1-9d10-1857c8653cee"
msgid "\\\"I'll be right here should you want to talk.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나는 여기에 있으니 말을 해.\\\""

msgctxt "1421d385-f9a3-4bd9-a546-43f8057052a8"
msgid ""
"\\\"I'd hoped to see Nazrielle's head on the chopping block, but since you're "
"here, I have a better idea. {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your "
"Highness}, would you like to hire a new weaponsmith? I'm aware you have a deal "
"with Nazrielle. But if you decide to break that deal and declare me the court's "
"master blacksmith... and allow me to keep Nazrielle as an assistant... oh, I could "
"never thank you enough! What do you say?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"나즈릴르의 머리를 자르고 싶었지만 네가 여기에 왔으니 더 좋은 생각이 있어. 나를 "
"새로운 대장장이로 임명해줘! 나즈릴르와 계약을 맺고 있다는 걸 알지만 계약을 깨고 나"
"를 새로운 대장장이로 임명하면... 그러면 나즈릴르는 내 조수가 되지... 그러면 정말 고"
"마울 텐데! 어떻게 생각해?\\\""

msgctxt "cdc18810-2359-47cc-8540-f56442a01981"
msgid ""
"\\\"So that's how it is. Very well. I was prepared for this turn of events. Let's "
"see how well you can handle my new friends.\\\" {n}Tiny stone animal figures "
"appear in Sartayne's hands. He scatters them all around him.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"그렇게 된 것이군. 좋아. 나는 준비가 되었지. 내 새로운 친구를 어떻게 다루나 보자"
"고.\\\" {n}Sartayne의 손에 작은 동물의 모습을 한 돌조각들이 나타납니다. 그는 그것들"
"을 주위에 뿌립니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "4360b0f0-acb8-47d6-95cc-0867799164a9"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne sneers and throws his hands up playfully.{/n} \\\"You got me! I "
"confess. Who figured it out? You or her? Anyway, that's not important right now. "
"Why did I do it? Purely for the sake of revenge. Years ago, she invested a lot of "
"effort in devastating my father, who was himself a well-known weaponsmith. He lost "
"everything that was dear to him: his reputation, his workshop – his whole life's "
"purpose.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 씨익 웃습니다.{/n} \\\"이런! 자백해야겠네. 누가 알아냈지? 너야? 그녀"
"야? 그건 중요하지 않아. 왜 내가 그랬냐고? 복수심 때문이지. 몇년 전 그녀는 유명한 대"
"장장이인 우리 아버지를 쓰러뜨리려 했지. 아버지는 명성과 대장간도 잃어버렸어.\\\""

msgctxt "f860ed8f-f750-4ea8-93c6-8d5853ef20fe"
msgid "\\\"Yes?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"응?\\\""

msgctxt "0ec411e6-e24c-4a4f-9383-fa844bc3fec3"
msgid ""
"\\\"I thought... I could... manage... as I took the blade, I had a feeling that "
"I... I was invincible... but this illusion... trick... oh, damn you... Nazrielle!\\"
"\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"나는... 이 검을 잡는 순간... 무적이라고 생각했는데... 하지만 그건... 망상이었"
"어... 젠장... 나즈릴르!\\\""

msgctxt "48d65dfc-abff-4a66-987f-094d62c915fc"
msgid "\\\"Help! Help me! I'm dying!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"도와줘! 제발! 나 죽네!\\\""

msgctxt "60523cd9-6168-46a9-a44d-31b1c31d938c"
msgid ""
"\\\"Hey, there's a rogue behind your back! Toss 'It' to me before he steals It!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 등 뒤에 도적이 있어! 그가 훔치기 전에 그것을 내게 넘겨!\\\""

msgctxt "437009e3-c2d6-45eb-b480-0866e4209210"
msgid "\\\"We can do this the easy way or the hard way!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"어렵게 하는 방법과 쉽게 하는 방법이 있지!\\\""

msgctxt "4f0b33b6-dd9b-4dea-b0f8-a0ff30bf8b5a"
msgid ""
"\\\"I'm a friend. Don't get me wrong, but that thing is playing tricks on your "
"mind. You must give it to me.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나는 친구야. 걱정할 것 없지만 생각이 많은 것 같군. 나를 믿으라고.\\\""

msgctxt "919080e7-9694-4c10-a731-0e9cad5efe5b"
msgid "\\\"Who the hell are you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너는 대체 누구지?\\\""

msgctxt "0b346c99-db2c-4e96-88b0-d235d8b17233"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"You should have given it to me willingly.\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"나에게 넘겼어야지.\\\""

msgctxt "27ce87f2-d291-41ea-886a-2baa7095b677"
msgid "\\\"Calm down, I'm leaving.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"진정해. 갈 테니까.\\\""

msgctxt "fd8e2bb6-7ff7-44aa-a7fe-63c79207ce19"
msgid ""
"{n}When he sees you, the elf crouches in fear, hiding something in his arms.{/n} \\"
"\"Have you come to take It? No! It's mine! Leave me alone!\\\" {n}A grimace of "
"pain and madness has captured his face.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프가 당신을 보자 겁에 질려 무언가를 숨깁니다.{/n} \\\"이걸 가지러 온 거야? 안 "
"돼! 이건 내 거야! 나를 내버려둬!\\\" {n}그의 얼굴은 고통과 광기로 덮여있습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "83d243b4-d3ff-41f9-b39c-587bd57eca34"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf tucks his head into his shoulders.{/n} \\\"Don't hurt me. Don't take it "
"away.\\\""
msgstr "{n}엘프는 머리를 수그립니다.{/n} \\\"나를 해치지 마. 가져가지 마.\\\""

msgctxt "e1c61b68-1684-4936-b757-7ac4974b35fe"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf tosses the thing before he knows he's been fooled.{/n} \\\"No! Thief! "
"Thief!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}그는 넘겨주고 나서야 자신이 속는다는 것을 압니다.{/n} \\\"안 돼! 도둑이야! 도둑!"
"\\\""

msgctxt "96483a66-49a6-4789-8fe6-c2a859a17456"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf turns around, startled, but doesn't let go of the thing in his hands.{/"
"n} \\\"Hey, are you trying to trick me? Thief!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 등을 돌리더니 놀라서 손에 있는 것을 넘겨주지 못합니다.{/n} \\\"이봐. 나"
"를 속이려는 거야? 이 도둑!\\\""

msgctxt "a6ff2a7b-d7a4-4531-bcd9-1271b4ef997f"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf freezes, then quickly throws away the thing, covers his head with his "
"arms and sobs:{/n} \\\"Thieves! Don't hurt me...\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 얼어붙어서는 그것을 던지고는 팔로 머리를 감싸고 흐느낍니다.{/n} \\\"도둑"
"이야! 나를 해치지 마...\\\""

msgctxt "6f143222-6261-4544-9a9b-2db943cfe895"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf is beginning to understand.{/n} \\\"I... Yes... It's bad! Poisoned my "
"mind!\\\" {n}The elf throws the thing away fiercely.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 이해하는 것 같습니다.{/n} \\\"나는... 그래... 그랬구나! 내가 헷갈렸어!\\"
"\" {n}엘프는 그것을 먼 곳으로 던져버립니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "55ac6286-3ebb-4a01-989a-f9dae41ad528"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf listens in astonishment.{/n} \\\"Me? Ditael... No! I am It's warden! I "
"served Nazrielle, and now I serve It! It is more important.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 듣고는 놀랍니다.{/n} \\\"나? Ditael... 안 돼! 그건 교도소장이었어! 나는 "
"나즈릴르를 섬기고 이제는 이걸 섬겨! 이게 더 중요해.\\\""

msgctxt "106cf79f-231d-4c5f-a78d-b10a85fb8961"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf is eyeing you apprehensively. He is ready to flee at any moment.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 알겠다는 듯 당신을 봅니다. 그는 언제라도 도망갈 준비가 되었습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "580c2ee4-35e9-4c9a-b1dc-c73fd273e318"
msgid ""
"\\\"It's far too valuable. You can't own It! I'm the only one who can! Do you hear "
"me? I'm the only one who can protect it! Everybody else wants It to themselves, "
"but I'm not giving It away! I've been hiding! I can hide from you, too. Don't come "
"closer!\\\" {n}The elf is staring at you, froth dripping from his lips.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"이건 정말 귀한 거야. 너에게 주지 않을 거야! 내 거니까! 알겠어? 나만이 이것을 보"
"호할 수 있다고! 모두가 이걸 가지길 원하지만 나는 주지 않겠어! 나는 숨어있었지. 너에"
"게서도 숨어있었어. 가까이 오지마!\\\" {n}엘프는 침을 흘리며 당신을 노려봅니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "5a14a822-705a-4489-89e6-3c85f47890c3"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf snaps at you with his teeth, doglike.{/n} \\\"Try to take it! I'll bite "
"off your fingers!\\\""
msgstr "{n}엘프는 이를 갑니다.{/n} \\\"가져가 보시지! 가져가면 물어줄 테다!\\\""

msgctxt "c88a76f4-f203-4674-9558-6ead4349da68"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf is beginning to understand.{/n} \\\"I... Yes... No! The thief is trying "
"to fool me! Go away! You can't have It! Thief!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 이해하기 시작합니다.{/n} \\\"나는... 그래... 아니야! 도둑이 나를 속이려 "
"한다! 저리 가! 너에게 안 줄 거야! 도둑아!\\\""

msgctxt "4b9771e5-5842-439d-8763-d7c8697e0ddf"
msgid ""
"{n}Ditael returns to his senses and falls limply onto the ground.{/n} \\\"Good "
"lord, it's finally over. The damned blade took my sanity... Oh, I never expected "
"Mistress Nazrielle could create such a monstrosity! Let her find herself another "
"assistant. This cursed thing nearly cost me my life.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Ditael은 제정신으로 돌아오고는 힘 없이 쓰러집니다.{/n} \\\"다행이야. 드디어 끝났"
"어. 이 저주 받은 검이 나를 미치게 했어... 나즈릴르가 이런 괴물을 만들 줄이야! 다른 "
"조수를 찾아보라고 전해줘. 이 저주 받은 물건 때문에 죽을 뻔했어.\\\""

msgctxt "cc335c13-cfd2-421a-8aad-cf50292ba380"
msgid "\\\"I agree to make a deal with you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너와 계약을 하지.\\\""

msgctxt "f31277c0-6fff-4695-b66b-2b5392a68538"
msgid "\\\"What do you have to offer?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"무엇을 제안할 거지?\\\""

msgctxt "0ce2a495-e1f0-4342-a5f0-63c6fbeea5d9"
msgid "\\\"Who are you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너는 누구야?\\\""

msgctxt "9f583ab5-2b47-4f50-a0cf-9ae89c62edaf"
msgid "\\\"I need to think.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"생각해보겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "e8978726-e321-4752-801e-270fddd2c86e"
msgid "\\\"I take no interest either in you or your weapons.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너나 그 무기에는 관심 없어.\\\""

msgctxt "ea655478-3ded-4970-8a95-12b0088c959d"
msgid ""
"{n}A stunning elven lady turns to you. Her hair is immaculate, and her eyes are "
"deep water. Her beauty is like a bird of prey. She is also heavily armed. As she "
"sees you, her superior air fades, leaving a charming smile on her face.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}놀랍도록 아름다운 엘프 여성이 당신을 봅니다. 그녀의 머리는 비단결 같고 그녀의 눈"
"은 깊은 호수와 같습니다. 그녀의 아름다움은 마치 한마리의 화려한 새 같습니다. 그녀"
"는 중무장을 했습니다. 당신을 보자 그녀의 위압적인 분위기는 사라지고 당신에게 매력적"
"인 미소를 짓습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "3f1971ea-76e1-410b-bbee-f220877497a9"
msgid ""
"{n}The elven lady nods politely.{/n} \\\"Will you help me? I promise, this deal "
"won't make you sorry.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프 여성이 끄덕입니다.{/n} \\\"나를 도와주겠어? 이 거래로 후회하지는 않을 거야."
"\\\""

msgctxt "d8845799-b5de-419d-b8e4-c037caf53347"
msgid ""
"\\\"Of course. Return to me immediately, if you decide to sign the contract.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"물론. 계약을 하고 싶다면 언제든지 찾아와.\\\""

msgctxt "32cd2611-77d5-4276-a9ee-9633611475c3"
msgid ""
"\\\"An artist, one of a kind. I create weapons. Not just pointy iron sticks, but "
"real weapons.\\\" {n}Nazrielle raises her eyebrows meaningfully.{/n} \\\"Alas, not "
"every domain appreciates high quality – and expensive – blades. I hope you'll be a "
"generous {mf|patron|patroness} and an appreciative {mf|connoisseur|connoisseuse}!\\"
"\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"예술가랄까. 나는 무기를 만들지. 끝이 뾰족한 쇠막대기가 아니라 진짜 무기 말이야."
"\\\" {n}나즈릴르는 말합니다.{/n} \\\"아. 고급 검을 아무나 쓸 수 있는 건 아니지. 네"
"가 취향이 고상한 후원자이길 바라.\\\""

msgctxt "30110097-5dab-4fcf-93bd-2e360ac9bc42"
msgid ""
"\\\"I hope to start serving you in exchange for your protection. You see, my "
"creations are not to everyone's liking. In the lands where I come from, demand for "
"artful blades is low. The heavier and cheaper ones are better for peasants. I had "
"to swallow my pride and do such work merely to survive.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"네 보호의 대가로 너를 섬기기로 했어. 내가 만든 것들을 모두가 좋아하지는 않아. "
"내가 온 곳에서는 좋은 검을 찾는 자가 많이 없지. 농부들에게는 무겁고 쌀 수록 더 좋"
"은 것이지. 나는 자존심을 팔고 먹고 살기 위해 그런 것들을 만들어야 했어.\\\""

msgctxt "b86236db-3a5d-4920-bb6a-58a8a449efd8"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle's eyes shine with excitement. She hands you a pen and paper.{/n} \\"
"\"Thank you! Sign here, please... and here. Done! All right! No one can touch a "
"court blacksmith! I will order my apprentices to pack up my materials and take "
"them to the new workshop, which you will kindly provide me with. As soon as I'm "
"settled, I'll send one of my people to deliver your order.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르의 눈은 흥분으로 빛납니다. 그녀는 종이와 펜을 건냅니다.{/n} \\\"고마워! "
"여기에 서명해줘... 그리고 여기에. 됐어! 좋아! 누구도 궁정 대장장이를 건들지 못 할 "
"거야! 내 도제를 시켜 짐을 챙겨오도록 할게. 네가 대장간을 넘겨준다면 말이야. 정착한 "
"후로 사람을 보내 네 주문을 받을게.\\\""

msgctxt "5583570d-ecf9-42e9-b3b2-10391e7f9e95"
msgid ""
"\\\"How fortunate! {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, allow "
"me to introduce myself. I am Nazrielle the weaponsmith. I can craft the deadliest "
"weapons mortals can make. I'd like to take the opportunity to pay my respects. As "
"soon as I found out you were here, I dispatched one of my apprentices, but of "
"course the bonehead failed his mission. Would you like to hear an offer that would "
"be to our mutual benefit?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"정말 운이 좋다! 내 소개를 할게. 나는 대장장이 나즈릴르야. 나는 가장 치명적인 무"
"기를 만들 수 있어. 내 능력을 증명할 기회를 줘. 네가 여기에 있다는 걸 알고 도제를 보"
"냈지만 만나지 못했지. 우리 서로 계약하지 않겠어?\\\""

msgctxt "eda4b5d6-1b1d-4a54-9828-866c156c5cf4"
msgid ""
"\\\"I know that serving you will allow me to earn true recognition! I'm offering "
"you a contract. You will provide me a workplace and all the necessary resources, "
"and I shall fill your arsenal with perfect instruments of death. More, I will "
"craft for you personally an amazing and deadly weapon, for which there is no "
"equal! I have long been looking for a warrior worthy of this masterpiece.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"너를 섬기는 게 좋을 거라 생각하고 있어! 이건 계약이야. 나에게 대장간과 필요한 "
"자원을 주면 완벽한 무기를 무기고에 채워넣어 줄게. 그리고 너만을 위한 치명적인 무기"
"를 만들어 줄 수 있어! 내 걸작을 써 줄 전사를 찾고 있었거든.\\\""

msgctxt "c2d13065-38b5-45d6-aa7e-e688ed24857a"
msgid ""
"{n}The elven lady bites her lip.{/n} \\\"That's a shame. Well, I'll be on my way – "
"to a place where my talents will be truly appreciated!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 입술을 깨뭅니다.{/n} \\\"그거 안 됐군. 그럼 나는 가겠어. 내 능력을 인정해"
"주는 자가 있는 곳으로.\\\""

msgctxt "e462565b-38fa-4c34-914c-41dd738cbc51"
msgid ""
"\\\"All you need to do is sign the contract and place your first order.\\\" {n}The "
"elven woman shows you a leather case with a prepared contract.{/n} \\\"Do we have "
"a deal?\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그냥 이 계약서에 서명하고 명령을 내리기만 하면 돼.\\\" {n}엘프 여성은 당신에게 "
"고급 가죽으로 장식된 계약서를 보여줍니다.{/n} \\\"계약 맺은 거야?\\\""

msgctxt "5488543d-894b-432a-870c-f65b696ec880"
msgid "\\\"I'd like to know more about you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에 대해 더 알고 싶어.\\\""

msgctxt "6e98632c-9a5b-4b0f-b826-fb8fff47e149"
msgid "\\\"You have one day to leave my domain.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"하루 줄 테니 나가.\\\""

msgctxt "16d7cdc1-c638-40ba-b27e-4a710baf5cb8"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about your craft.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 능력에 대해 말해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "bd699b7a-7f90-490b-b17b-9f17a725799e"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about yourself.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에 대해 말해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "ebf0233d-00bd-4644-999f-66df7467aef7"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about your apprentices.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너의 도제에 대해 말해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "7e0acc16-c2d6-495e-8fea-1e849d65b304"
msgid "\\\"Let us discuss it later.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"그건 나중에 얘기하지.\\\""

msgctxt "0f7c3828-d692-49e0-af41-3a2933591260"
msgid "\\\"I heard the news that one of your assistants has gone missing.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 보조 중 한명이 사라졌다는 얘기를 들었어.\\\""

msgctxt "8b879c00-c8dc-4c53-8bf0-b65a23b27c7e"
msgid ""
"\\\"Take away this dangerous thing. It poisoned the mind of one of your assistants."
"\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이 위험한 물건은 치워. 이건 네 보조의 정신을 아프게 해.\\\""

msgctxt "61fc8a31-57e4-4de5-bd15-de163ffc9a99"
msgid ""
"\\\"Sartayne is dead. He had a vendetta against you for bankrupting his father.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"Sartayne이 죽었어. 자신의 아버지의 복수를 꿈꾸고 있더군.\\\""

msgctxt "e8939990-99ed-457a-a158-2846d5e66ae1"
msgid "\\\"You owe Sartayne. I set him free.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너는 Sartayne에게 빚 졌어. 나는 그를 풀어줬지.\\\""

msgctxt "efa073d2-b588-4389-88c8-3bfc8fab4c79"
msgid ""
"\\\"The goods you've been selling are cursed. Would you like to explain yourself?\\"
"\""
msgstr "\\\"네가 판 물건들이 저주받았어. 어떻게 된 일인지 설명해봐.\\\""

msgctxt "1d9ec33e-5005-40ad-8404-464cf4512013"
msgid "\\\"How are the things going in the blacksmith shop?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"요즘 대장간은 어때?\\\""

msgctxt "d20145dd-cc08-467f-a929-73450349a85b"
msgid ""
"{n}A heavily armed {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} eyes you suspiciously, but she sounds "
"welcoming enough.{/n} \\\"Welcome! My apprentice Sartayne just finished unpacking, "
"but I'm already up and running – all the better to serve you!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}중무장한 {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}는 당신을 의심스럽게 보지만 당신을 환영합니다."
"{/n} \\\"어서 와! 내 도제 Sartayne이 막 짐을 풀었지만 아직 장사는 못 할 것 같아.\\"
"\""

msgctxt "10c0da23-2677-4e18-b35e-349acc62d63f"
msgid ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} is gazing at you almost without blinking, like an owl."
"{/n} \\\"How can I help you?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}는 눈도 깜빡하지 않고 당신을 봅니다.{/n} \\\"내가 어떻"
"게 도와줄까?\\\""

msgctxt "3856f2e6-0fee-4a89-b903-f54623ddaff4"
msgid ""
"{n}This time {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} looks different. There's still fire in her "
"eyes, but her face expresses humility and obedience. Her shoulders are slumped. "
"There's a bruise on her cheek. Her voice is quiet and servile.{/n} \\\"Welcome! "
"Master Sartayne is busy at the forge. I will do my best to serve you.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}이번에 {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}는 다르게 보입니다. 그녀의 눈이 불타오르고 있지"
"만 표정은 시무룩합니다. 그녀의 어깨가 처집니다. 그녀의 뺨에는 멍이 들었습니다. 그녀"
"의 목소리는 조용합니다.{/n} \\\"어서 와. Sartayne 주인님은 지금 바쁘셔. 대신 내가 "
"필요한 걸 줄게.\\\""

msgctxt "4d5b03b5-c33d-4e42-9052-dcb172d1d0f0"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle lowers her eyes and bites her lip.{/n} \\\"I am but dust in the wind. "
"I'm not worthy of your attention... {mf|sire|mistress}.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 눈을 깔고는 입술을 깨뭅니다.{/n} \\\"나는 바람 속의 먼지에 지나지 않"
"아. 나는 쓸모 없는 년이야.\\\""

msgctxt "b01a3e73-94c7-45d4-9b37-225325451da2"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle tucks her head into her shoulders.{/n} \\\"I will pass this message "
"along to the master. It will make him angry.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 허리를 펴고 말합니다.{/n} \\\"이 소식을 주인님께 전할게. 주인님이 화"
"가 날 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "c9476068-8b34-41dd-a837-9e8e720d1508"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle is eyeing you apprehensively.{/n} \\\"So, you wish to break our "
"contract? This is most unfortunate. You will hardly find a master as skilled as I "
"am, but that doesn't seem to trouble you. Farewell.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 알겠다는 듯 당신을 봅니다.{/n} \\\"그러니까 계약을 끝내고 싶다고? 정"
"말 안 됐군. 나 처럼 실력 있는 장인은 찾기 힘들 테지만 너에게는 문제가 되지 않는 것 "
"같군. 안녕히.\\\""

msgctxt "03fed43c-d0bc-4ac5-ad3e-6aa9af2898e6"
msgid "\\\"What exactly would you like to know?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"무엇을 알고 싶은 거지?\\\""

msgctxt "6f80d3ce-621e-4496-aaee-cd371075d18c"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle looks at you suspiciously for a moment, and then nervously brushes "
"her fingers through her hair.{/n} \\\"My weapons define me. I've been drawn to it "
"since I was a child. I have over three hundred blades at home, each of them "
"special. I wanted to be a professional weaponsmith, so I learned the craft from "
"greatest masters of Kyonin.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 잠시 당신을 의심스럽게 보고는 불안한 듯 손가락으로 머리를 꼬읍니다.{/"
"n} \\\"내 무기로 나는 인정을 받지. 나는 어렸을 때부터 일했어. 나는 집에 삼백자루의 "
"칼이 있고 모두가 특별하지. 나는 전문 대장장이가 되고 싶어서 쿄닌에서 가장 유명한 장"
"인에게서 배웠어.\\\""

msgctxt "da0dd69c-23e4-4dc8-83bc-d0795c3b856d"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle juts out her chin.{/n} \\\"My art! A mere craftsman would attach a "
"piece of wood to a piece of iron, and be happy with their work. That's not how I "
"do it. I listen to a weapon. I talk to it. I spark its desire for blood and "
"violence. This gives you two warriors in the battlefield, the soldier and their "
"sword.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 턱을 빼듭니다.{/n} \\\"내 작품이야! 그냥 단순한 검은 나무 막대기에 쇠"
"를 꽂은 것이지. 하지만 나는 그렇게 하지 않아. 나는 무기의 소리를 듣지. 나는 무기와 "
"대화를 해. 피와 죽음을 원하는 칼의 욕망을 불어넣어. 이걸 부하에게 주면 칼과 부하 각"
"각 둘의 부하를 얻는 것과 같아.\\\""

msgctxt "bb3241fe-666d-479e-ba43-93216ebc21f4"
msgid "\\\"Always at your service.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"말만 해.\\\""

msgctxt "89857877-199c-499b-9c76-fb8ef6868a80"
msgid ""
"{n}The elven woman waves her hand angrily.{/n} \\\"The boneheads? Why would you "
"care about them? Ah, it doesn't matter anyway. I recruit apprentices for simple "
"tasks. They sign my contracts. They obey me and take full responsibility for any "
"harm they suffer during service. One of them, Sartayne, works in the smithy. The "
"other, Ditael, tests finished weapons and runs errands.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프 여성은 손사래를 칩니다.{/n} \\\"그 멍청이들을? 왜 그런 녀석들을 신경 써? 상"
"관 없어. 나는 심부름 하는 도제를 고용했어. 그들은 계약을 했어. 그들은 내 말이라면 "
"곧이 곧대로 순종하지. 도제 중 하나인 Sartayne는 대장간 일을 도와. 다른 도제 Ditael"
"는 완성된 무기를 시험하고 심부름을 하지.\\\""

msgctxt "d1fc23ac-1712-41cf-a249-4a280000d0c7"
msgid ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle's{/d} face is contorted in desperation. Her eyes have a "
"haunted look.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}… To "
"what do we owe the pleasure?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle's{/d}의 얼굴은 절망스럽게 구겨집니다. 그녀의 눈은 퀭합니다."
"{/n} \\\"어서 와... 뭐가 필요해?\\\""

msgctxt "8f2f48d9-3176-4fb3-ba66-03cb3f2d9fa2"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle looks at you in disbelief. She spits on the ground in a most non-"
"elfish way, gives you a scornful look, and instead of bidding you farewell, says:{/"
"n} \\\"Everyone along my path will know that your word is worthless.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 절망스럽게 당신을 봅니다. 그녀는 엘프답지 않게 땅에 침을 뱉고는 인사"
"하는 대신 당신을 험악하게 봅니다.{/n} \\\"나와 같은 길을 걸은 사람들은 네가 쓰레기"
"라는 걸 알 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "3609890b-619a-433a-b853-e6b9526f7de8"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle falls silent for a few seconds, looking very focused. Then she smiles "
"slowly and malevolently:{/n} \\\"What a spectacular day. Thank you.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 집중하며 잠시 침묵합니다. 그리고는 천천히 웃습니다.{/n} \\\"정말 놀라"
"운 날이야. 고마워.\\\""

msgctxt "913bb521-660c-46d9-ac5f-7593fb5e5e26"
msgid ""
"{n}The elven woman carefully takes the blade from your hands. She bows politely. "
"There's honey in her voice.{/n} \\\"I'm terribly sorry. What an unbelievable "
"failure! I would never have allowed a faulty blade to get into your hands! That's "
"what we need quality control for, right?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프 여성은 조심스럽게 당신의 손에서 칼을 받습니다. 그녀는 예의 바르게 인사합니"
"다. 그녀의 목소리는 달콤합니다.{/n} \\\"정말 미안해. 믿을 수 없어! 네 손에 실패한 "
"작품을 쥐어주다니! 이래서 애프터 서비스가 중요한 거겠지?\\\""

msgctxt "822c4b24-d3e0-4715-be67-4e41e807d2d5"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle winces, and looks embarrassed.{/n} \\\"It's so humiliating that "
"you've learned of it. Something went wrong with my weapon. It was... hm... It was "
"meant to be a gift for you. But Ditael went crazy as he took it. He fell into a "
"fury and ran off. If a faulty blade with my mark gets into someone else's hands, "
"my reputation will be ruined.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 찡그리더니 당황한 표정을 짓습니다.{/n} \\\"정말 부끄럽군. 내 무기가 "
"뭔가 잘못 되었어. 이건... 흠... 이건 선물이었는데. 하지만 Ditael이 무기를 잡자마자 "
"미쳐버렸어. 그는 화를 내며 도망갔지. 내 표식이 찍힌 무기가 잘못 되면 내 명성에 금"
"이 갈 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "b6d87dd5-c063-4792-8359-39bb3412255f"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle turns pale as paper.{/n} \\\"Cursed? Oh goodness... It wasn't me! I "
"didn't do it! It's simply impossible! My creations are impeccable! I'm a master, "
"you know! Such a thing has never happened in my entire life! Nobody could...\\"
"\" {n}The elven woman falls silent, her lips move, but she doesn't make a sound.{/"
"n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 종잇장처럼 새하얘집니다.{/n} \\\"저주 받았다고? 오. 세상에... 그건 내"
"가 아니야! 나는 그런 짓을 하지 않아! 이럴 리가 없는데! 내 작품이 저주 받다니! 나는 "
"장인인 거 너도 알잖아! 내 인생에서 이런 일은 일어나지 않았어! 누구도...\\\" {n}엘"
"프 여성은 침묵하고는 중얼거리지만 말하지 않습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "44c4aa14-4dfa-42d7-81fe-f149fe1c4231"
msgid ""
"\\\"But then my comrades in craft and I... We had a bit of a falling out. A few "
"bastards dared to question my skill. I felt that I could only shed this burden "
"outside Kyonin. And you know what? I swore then that I would prove that I'm head "
"and shoulders above them! Two of them paid the price even when I was working back "
"home. They couldn't stand the competition and went bankrupt. – That's where all my "
"competition is headed!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"하지만 동료와 내가... 우리는 약간 다툼이 있었어. 멍청이 몇녀석이 감히 내 실력"
"에 대해 뭐라 하더군. 나는 쿄닌을 벋어나야 이 짐을 벗을 거라 생각했지. 그리고 말이"
"지. 나는 그들보다 뛰어나다는 걸 증명하고 싶었어! 내가 돌아갔을 때 그들 중 둘은 대가"
"를 치우었지. 그들은 경쟁하지 못하고 파산한 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "a58a2bca-05e6-4c90-8301-044dd07a66d5"
msgid ""
"\\\"I beg you, {mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, help me! I "
"don't think this idiot could have gone far. He may still be near the river. Bring "
"me back the blade, and I will never let you down again, I swear!\\\" {n}The elven "
"woman falls silent. She frowns, as if trying to remember something.{/n} \\\"Oh! "
"But of course! Please be sure to save Ditael, my other apprentice. If it's not too "
"much trouble.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"부탁이야. 나를 도와줘! 이 바보가 멀리는 못 갔을 거야. 아마 강 주위에 있을 거"
"야. 나에게 검을 가져다주면 너를 다시는 실망시키지 않을게!\\\" {n}엘프 여성은 침묵합"
"니다. 그는 무언가 떠올리려는 듯 얼굴을 찡그립니다.{/n} \\\"오! 물론이지! Ditael도 "
"구해주겠다고 약속해줘. 문제가 되지 않는다면 말이야.\\\""

msgctxt "ab296bdb-1e8e-44c8-b2ae-3106e1e0df38"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle recovers her voice, and now sounds strangely calm.{/n} \\\"It's "
"Sartayne. It's him. He's been spoiling my work. No one else could do it. The "
"little bastard tried to tarnish my name.\\\" {n}There's nothing but cold hatred in "
"Nazrielle's gaze. The tone of her voice is quiet and murderous.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 목소리를 가다듬었고 이상하게 그녀는 침착해 보입니다.{/n} \\\"그건 "
"Sartayne야. 그 녀석이야. 그 녀석이 내 작품을 망쳤어. 누구도 그런 짓을 하지 않아. "
"그 조그만한 멍청이가 내 이름에 먹칠을 했어.\\\" {n}나즈릴르의 눈에서는 차가운 분노"
"가 보입니다. 그녀의 목소리는 조용하지만 섬뜩합니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "ed082e9f-056f-4b60-994f-b84a2d531add"
msgid ""
"\\\"By the right granted to me by our agreement, I am calling upon {mf|Your Grace|"
"Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}! Sartayne insulted the reputation of the "
"master, to whom you promised protection. I asking you to find and kill the "
"bastard. He must be hiding in his hut not far from the capital.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"계약에 의해 부탁할게! Sartayne가 너의 장인의 명성에 먹질을 했어. 그 멍청이를 찾"
"아 죽여줘. 그는 수도에서 멀지 않은 자신의 오두막에 숨어있을 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "dded5550-2d7a-4069-acf4-690fbcd63e29"
msgid ""
"\\\"I promise you will receive your gift. Please, give me a little more time. I "
"hope the items I send with Sartayne will fend off boredom while you await the "
"arrival of the true masterpiece!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"너에게 보상은 해줄게. 제발 내게 더 시간을 줘. Sartayne와 함께 보낸 아이템들은 "
"진정한 걸작이 나오기 전까지는 지루함을 달래기 좋을 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "0fe714a5-c8e4-4b8d-8ae4-a518f72caab2"
msgid ""
"\\\"Of course, I pay close attention to detail. A sharper bevel will allow the "
"blade to cut through the flesh, not into it. Change the angle of the point, and "
"the blade will pierce through armor like a stitching awl without sliding. I "
"learned all this from weapons. You just need to be able to know what you're "
"looking at.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"물론. 나는 디테일이 중요하다고 생각해. 대충 만든 검은 살을 가르지만 파고들지는 "
"못해. 검의 끝을 다르게 만들면 검은 빗나가는 것도 없이 바늘 처럼 갑옷 속을 꿰뚫을 "
"수 있지. 나는 무기를 보고 연구했어. 네가 원하는 무기도 찾을 수 있을 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "677ba513-25d2-49ff-ad4f-4cac08be08f4"
msgid ""
"\\\"Excellent! Wonderful! I fired my apprentices. I've had enough with Sartayne. I "
"work longer hours, of course, but every blade that leaves my forge is my personal "
"responsibility now.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"좋았어! 훌륭해! 나는 내 도제를 해고했어. 나는 Sartayne와 관계를 정리했어. 대장"
"간을 떠난 검은 내 자존심이 달려있으니 더 오래 일했어.\\\""

msgctxt "30512b0f-9e8f-4081-824e-fdecc29fdfb8"
msgid ""
"This deadly blade was crafted by a true master. The blow never deviates one iota "
"and leaves a very clean cut. Equally good in combat for piercing the enemy's armor "
"and on the scaffold for decapitating a criminal."
msgstr ""
"이 날카로운 검은 진정한 장인에 의해 만들어졌습니다. 이 검으로 찌르면 목표를 아주 깨"
"끗하게 가릅니다. 적의 갑옷을 꿰뚫기에도 좋은 검입니다."

msgctxt "696a8356-dbf1-458b-868c-1891cf8e3da3"
msgid "Right of the Powerful"
msgstr "강한 자의 옳음"

msgctxt "9c5589b1-fac1-438c-b08e-487be9ffd35a"
msgid ""
"This weapon was supposed to cast fear on enemies, but for some unknown reason it "
"poisoned the mind of its first owner. The curse has since lost its power, and the "
"sword has now turned into an ordinary blade."
msgstr ""
"이 무기는 적들의 공포를 자아내지만 어떤 이유로 인해 이 무기를 처음 쥔 자의 정신을 "
"미치게 했습니다. 저주가 풀린 이후에는 평범한 검에 지나지 않습니다."

msgctxt "bbe6e8f0-4073-4abf-b30d-0e2604734424"
msgid "Nazrielle's Cursed Sword"
msgstr "나즈릴르의 저주받은 검"

msgctxt "31ad45a4-1483-4fb9-9347-decbf9858cb6"
msgid ""
"Something strange is going on in the region. Residents complain of a strange "
"misfortune that is plaguing their homes and their work. Someone must be casting "
"spells to harm the {mf|baron's|baroness'|King's|Queen's} subjects. The reason "
"behind this must be found, along with the guilty party.\\nCan be fixed by: Warden, "
"Magister, High Priest\\nWarden, Magister, High Priest:\\nGF-F: The Advisor's "
"agents failed to find the source of the calamity. It sounds like only minor "
"annoyances, but where are they coming from? The people continue to complain of "
"misfortune. This means the investigation is far from over.\\nS-GS: The Advisor's "
"agents found the source of the problem. All the harmful items were purchased from "
"Nazrielle, the weaponsmith!"
msgstr ""
"이 지역에 이상한 일이 일어나고 있습니다. 지역 주민들이 불행을 겪어 집과 일터에서 힘"
"든 일을 겪었습니다. 누군가 당신의 백성들에게 마법을 건 것이 분명합니다. 이유는 아"
"직 알려지지 않았습니다.\\n이것은 이들이 해결할 수 있습니다. Warden, Magister, High "
"Priest\\nWarden, Magister, High Priest:\\nGF-F: 조언자의 요원이 마법의 근원을 찾는 "
"것을 실패했습니다. 도대체 그것들은 어디에서 온 것일까요? 사람들은 계속해서 불행을 "
"겪습니다. 조사는 아직 끝나지 않았습니다.\\nS-GS: 조언자의 요원이 문제의 근원을 발견"
"했습니다. 모든 해로운 무기들은 대장장이 나즈릴르가 구매했습니다!"

msgctxt "c943189c-0543-42f9-9ab5-bd2c9df7bcbc"
msgid "\\\"I expect a gift worthy of the favor you've been shown.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네가 보여준 호의에 맞먹는 선물이야.\\\""

msgctxt "c7a4e7e8-cf94-432c-aa97-4527d3258236"
msgid "\\\"You respect our deal. That's commendable.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"우리의 계약은 중요하지. 나도 동의해.\\\""

msgctxt "002d1b4e-e3d6-4a09-8b02-f70f6bad6963"
msgid "\\\"I want something from you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에게서 원하는 것이 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "d692c95b-71e8-4a1f-a708-f0eb1f81cf4f"
msgid ""
"\\\"I declare you persona non grata. Leave my lands, or you will be punished.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너에게 최후통첩을 하지. 내 땅을 떠나지 않으면 혼날 줄 알아.\\\""

msgctxt "915f3613-b88f-48ef-8856-9b7ff890bcca"
msgid "\\\"I need a sword that's swift and tough.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"날카롭고 튼튼한 검을 원해.\\\""

msgctxt "9319f4af-b3d9-4224-ba9e-3efa46e92090"
msgid "\\\"I need a dagger that's invisible and deadly.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"숨기기 좋은 치명적인 단검을 원해.\\\""

msgctxt "ab214e8a-59d7-4d28-9fae-158b389e420a"
msgid "\\\"I could use some flexible and sturdy chainmail.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"편안하고 튼튼한 사슬 갑옷을 원해.\\\""

msgctxt "3872920e-4484-4838-8520-a45b4aac89cb"
msgid "\\\"I need something that can increase my speed.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내 속도를 올려줄 아이템을 원해.\\\""

msgctxt "86fb515f-cde0-47c0-8bfd-69de37bbc18c"
msgid "\\\"I'd like a sample of elven metalwork.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"엘프가 만든 쇠붙이 샘플을 원해.\\\""

msgctxt "57a213f9-13dc-4ca9-a669-39e45c9f500d"
msgid "\\\"Decide for yourself how you might surprise me.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나를 놀라게 할 물건 아무거나.\\\""

msgctxt "3c675c1c-e74a-48a6-b948-987472fb0587"
msgid ""
"{n}For the first time, Nazrielle arrives in person to deliver her gifts. She's "
"clearly anxious.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, I "
"once again apologize for the dirty tricks that Sartayne pulled. I would like to "
"repay your good graces with a truly magnificent gift. But forging it will take "
"time. Meanwhile, please accept this modest present. It isn't spoiled. I checked it "
"three times.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}처음으로 나즈릴르는 직접 자신의 선물을 전달하러 왔습니다. 그는 불안해 보입니다."
"{/n} \\\"안녕. Sartayne가 저지른 일에 대해 사과하고 싶었어. 네 친절함을 보답할 좋"
"은 선물을 하고 싶어. 하지만 만드는 데 시간이 걸릴 거야. 하지만 이 작은 선물을 받아"
"줘. 이건 저주 받지 않았어. 세번이나 확인했거든.\\\""

msgctxt "344b99c2-22ae-4bed-b495-808d27c934eb"
msgid ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} bows ceremoniously.{/n} \\\"In accordance with our "
"agreement, I have brought you a gift which serves as payment for your protection.\\"
"\""
msgstr ""
"{n}{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}는 인사합니다.{/n} \\\"계약에 의해 보호를 해준 보답으로 "
"선물을 가져왔어.\\\""

msgctxt "425025e9-ba00-4c59-94ac-82bee913f0a3"
msgid ""
"{n}With an elegant gesture, the elven lady hands you a package.{/n} \\\"I hope you "
"will appreciate the quality of this gift. It is better than any weapon the local "
"masters can produce.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}우아한 동작으로 엘프 여성은 당신에게 선물을 건냅니다.{/n} \\\"이 선물을 좋아했으"
"면 좋겠어. 이 지역 장인들이 만든 어느 것보다도 더 좋은 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "7f688bb2-f9bf-49ec-b291-2d307f895b34"
msgid ""
"{n}A beautiful blade appears in elven lady's hands.{/n} \\\"I named this blade the "
"Enforcer. Its blows are decisive and crushing. It is the embodiment of justice. "
"Strict, severe – remorseless. It will not hesitate to take any life, if {mf|Your "
"Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness} so desires.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프 여성의 손에 아름다운 검이 들려져있습니다.{/n} \\\"나는 이 검의 이름을 "
"Enforcer라고 지었어. 이 검은 피하기도 힘들고 강력하기도 하지. 튼튼해서 날이 나갈 일"
"도 없어. 네가 원한다면 이걸로 어떤 자의 생명이든 뺏을 수 있을 거야. 이걸로 정의를 "
"구현해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "24d34211-bb3f-4a0d-adbd-000fbd5bd0ab"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne bows, polite but not obsequious.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|"
"Your Highness|Your Highness}, I have come to thank you for the favor you did me. I "
"appreciate your protection, and I will make sure you're always satisfied with my "
"work.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 예의바르지만 당당하게 인사합니다.{/n} \\\"안녕! 나에게 베풀어준 친절"
"을 보답하러 왔어. 보호해주어 고맙고 언제나 항상 너를 만족시키기 위해 최선을 다 할 "
"거야.\\\""

msgctxt "4be3b43d-2658-4d94-a37d-256b72252736"
msgid "{n}Nazrielle nods slowly.{/n} \\\"I am all ears.\\\""
msgstr "{n}나즈릴르는 천천히 고개를 끄덕입니다.{/n} \\\"잘 듣고 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "cf9cbf58-72f5-4679-ba9b-89f2d5abf0db"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle frowns and lowers her head.{/n} \\\"I'm sorry it turned out this way. "
"But I must obey your orders.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 얼굴을 찡그리고 고개를 숙입니다.{/n} \\\"이렇게 되어 미안해. 하지만 "
"네 부탁이 더 중요하지.\\\""

msgctxt "414e4b16-6460-4c71-b355-aaecbaf892ad"
msgid ""
"{n}Nazrielle sighs with relief.{/n} \\\"I appreciate the opportunity to make up "
"for my mistakes. I can assure you, I never exaggerated my skill when I referred to "
"myself as the best weaponsmith. You'll see it for yourself. Very soon.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}나즈릴르는 안도의 한숨을 쉽니다.{/n} \\\"내 실수를 되돌릴 기회를 주어 고마워. 내"
"가 최고의 대장장이라고 불리는 것은 과장이 아니야. 기대해도 좋아.\\\""

msgctxt "c28fdb4d-1ddd-4a4c-bf07-8e666d8cf98f"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne grins.{/n} \\\"I admit, I don't give a damn about agreements. I "
"respect the right of the powerful, and I don't want to suffer {d|Nazriel}"
"Nazrielle{/d}'s fate.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 웃습니다.{/n} \\\"좋아. 나는 상관하지 않겠어. 나는 그 검이 뛰어나다"
"고 생각하고 {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}를 방해하고 싶지 않아.\\\""

msgctxt "58706bc6-bacf-4b4a-bf30-45714d92c7b3"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne raises his eyebrow ironically.{/n} \\\"So, you don't like me. Well, "
"that's a shame. I'm leaving, but with my head held high, knowing that I've taken "
"my vengeance. The one who devastated my father has been humiliated and dishonored, "
"and it was you who helped me. I am grateful to you. Farewell.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 놀랍니다.{/n} \\\"내가 싫다는 거지? 안타깝군. 나는 떠나지만 복수를 하"
"게 되어 만족해. 내 아버지를 망친 녀석의 이름에 먹칠을 했고 너는 나를 도왔으니까. 고"
"마워. 안녕.\\\""

msgctxt "393266a2-e899-418b-9b1d-05152b26a9c6"
msgid ""
"\\\"This blade will split a horse's hair and troll's skin. I'll make sure of it.\\"
"\""
msgstr "\\\"이 검이 괴물의 가죽을 꿰뚫을 거야. 확실해.\\\""

msgctxt "59152a7c-9712-4791-9449-16c6e61f6bcf"
msgid ""
"\\\"Rest assured, my lady apprentice and I won't disappoint you. Nazrielle will "
"work very carefully on our little present for you. Otherwise... Oh, no! Of course, "
"she takes such good care of her skilled hands. She'd never risk losing a single "
"pretty finger.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"우리는 너를 실망시키지 않겠어. 나즈릴르는 너에게 줄 선물을 만들기 위해 노력하"
"고 있으니까. 오. 이런! 그녀는 자신의 손을 그렇게 아껴. 손가락이 다치기라도 하면 안 "
"되니까.\\\""

msgctxt "d9a7776a-a26f-40a4-8265-e3cef893b0bb"
msgid ""
"\\\"Speed and defense are equally important to a warrior. You shouldn't sacrifice "
"one for the sake of the other. Better to keep both.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"속도와 방어는 전사에게 중요하지. 하나를 위해 다른 것을 희생할 필요는 없어. 두가"
"지 모두를 챙기면 되지.\\\""

msgctxt "5944d225-a4cb-4d7c-b8df-01f8718f8a3f"
msgid ""
"\\\"My people have been honing their talents for an eternity. Elven craftsmanship "
"is always the best.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"우리 엘프들은 영원히 재능을 연마하지. 엘프의 기술은 최고야.\\\""

msgctxt "9f6af82b-27cf-4c0e-b58f-3b01dc524433"
msgid "\\\"I'm doing my best to serve you.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"최선을 다할게.\\\""

msgctxt "d7b9d2d5-6099-42b8-83c3-944b949542ea"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne bows gracefully and smiles slightly, looking at you.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your "
"Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, I am proud to give you this gift. I "
"hope you will find it useful.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 우아하게 인사하고 당신을 보며 미소를 짓습니다.{/n} \\\"너에게 이걸 선"
"물하게 되어 기뻐. 잘 사용했으면 좋겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "d7fbf950-5f94-4f85-8171-1bf9cfd7ee63"
msgid "{n}Sartayne readily shifts forward. There's a quiet smile on his face.{/n}"
msgstr "{n}Sartayne는 조용히 미소짓습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "72269852-fb51-4d2e-9576-172c24fee6da"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne bows very politely.{/n} \\\"{mf|Your Grace|Your Grace|Your Highness|"
"Your Highness}, I have brought gifts to repay you for your protection.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 예의바르게 인사합니다.{/n} \\\"네 보호에 대한 보답으로 선물을 가져왔"
"어.\\\""

msgctxt "205663a9-3678-4605-980b-76be861a6c15"
msgid "\\\"Who are you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너는 누구지?\\\""

msgctxt "6551dd32-ace2-44e2-87c3-bd02fe4a55ed"
msgid "\\\"Tell me about Nazrielle.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나즈릴르에 대해 말해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "13c01697-16dd-4979-b2c8-ef1bf79c878b"
msgid "\\\"I'll see what I can do.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내가 할 수 있는 일을 찾아보겠어.\\\""

msgctxt "98a853f8-b197-48c9-a960-9f285e16c45d"
msgid "\\\"Does Nazrielle mistreat you?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나즈릴르가 너를 괴롭혔나?\\\""

msgctxt "b1101128-8805-4c64-8a54-fdbcb16ced65"
msgid "\\\"What gift are you talking about?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"무슨 선물을 말하는 거지?\\\""

msgctxt "845a69a6-1923-4d6c-a7cc-5cc163ae5e72"
msgid "\\\"Extend my gratitude to Nazrielle.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내 감사의 인사를 나즈릴르에게 전해줘.\\\""

msgctxt "a6f43323-377b-429b-a74d-4888cca4d0e1"
msgid "\\\"I have a specific request to your mistress.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네 주인에게 특별한 요청을 하고 싶어.\\\""

msgctxt "c88e2906-99da-4683-830d-2207377e619a"
msgid "\\\"Nazrielle has one day to leave my domain.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나즈릴르는 내일까지 내 땅을 떠나야 할 거야.\\\""

msgctxt "9b1eed58-fbab-4111-a815-95f3cecb617d"
msgid "\\\"I need a dagger that's invisible and deadly.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "be688032-5358-4c0d-99ba-21389f405865"
msgid "\\\"I could certainly use some flexible and sturdy chainmail.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "e3782bd8-f0be-41aa-9b69-32716a87f2d6"
msgid ""
"\\\"Is there anything Nazrielle can do to make me swifter on the battlefield?\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3fdcd20f-34ec-47e8-a3b9-7075a22e08aa"
msgid "\\\"I'd like a sample of her elven metalwork.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27c6fa75-c37a-493b-96e1-53553794b26e"
msgid "\\\"I've changed my mind. Let Nazrielle think of something herself.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2309200e-60ae-4e58-968b-0559bdf54c4c"
msgid "\\\"I need a sword that's swift and tough.\\\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "f78df191-f5d2-4a39-83e0-81e0044caf38"
msgid ""
"{n}A pathetic-looking elf stands before you. His clothes are wrinkled, his cheek "
"is scratched, and his nose is swollen like he's suffered a heavy blow. He glances "
"around with a haunted look, and bows.{/n} \\\"My name is Sartayne. Mistress {d|"
"Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} was supposed to have given me a gift for {mf|Your Grace|Your "
"Grace|Your Highness|Your Highness}, but... I'm afraid, we might have a bit of a "
"problem here...\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}후줄근한 옷을 입은 엘프가 당신 앞에 서있습니다. 그의 옷은 구겨졌고 그는 구타를 "
"당했는지 코가 부어있고 얼굴에 상처가 났습니다. 그는 멍한 표정으로 당신에게 인사합니"
"다.{/n} \\\"나는 Sartayne야. {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} 주인님이 네게 줄 선물을 가져"
"다 주라고 했어... 하지만 문제가 하나 있는 것 같아...\\\""

msgctxt "d8eb3b83-da8c-4c78-ad85-0f7987d776e0"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf eyes you in astonishment.{/n} \\\"Me? I'm Sartayne, assistant and "
"servant of Mistress Nazrielle. She teaches me her craft. I've been dreaming of "
"becoming a weaponsmith ever since I was a child. My father was a master, too. His "
"swords were famous. Unfortunately, he went bankrupt while I was still too young to "
"learn. He withered away and never got to teach me his skills. But the Mistress "
"gave me another chance!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 놀라서 당신을 봅니다.{/n} \\\"나? 나는 나즈릴르의 조수 Sartayne야. 그녀"
"는 나에게 기술을 가르치지. 나는 어렸을 때부터 대장장이가 되는 꿈을 꾸었어. 우리 아"
"버지도 장인이었지. 그의 검은 유명해. 불행히도 내가 기술을 배우기도 전에 그는 파산했"
"지. 그는 약해져서 나에게 기술을 가르치지 못했어. 하지만 나즈릴르가 나에게 기회를 "
"준 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "7cfa692e-279e-40f7-abbd-4bfa5cdcc277"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf's enthusiasm is almost pathetic.{/n} \\\"I'm Mistress Nazrielle's "
"assistant. It's a great honor! She's a genius! Her knowledge of weapons knows no "
"bounds. Although... although it's scary sometimes, you know. Anyway, I'm not "
"complaining. I'm happy to serve her.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프의 광기는 불쌍해보이기까지 합니다.{/n} \\\"나는 나즈릴르 주인님의 조수야. 그"
"건 나의 영광이지! 그녀는 천재야! 그녀의 무기 지식은 무한해. 하지만... 가끔은 무섭"
"지. 그래도 나는 불평하지 않아. 나는 그녀를 섬기는 것이 좋아.\\\""

msgctxt "133b1670-8ae9-4fcf-acf3-3d3a1b6a2fe5"
msgid "{n}The elf bows low once again.{/n}"
msgstr "{n}엘프는 다시 인사합니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "f91755f2-51a1-47c5-906a-f1d93bef3a89"
msgid ""
"\\\"Mistress Nazrielle has been working hard on a special gift for you. But one of "
"her apprentices, Ditael, went mad after he touched the blade that was meant to be "
"presented to you. He grabbed it and just ran off as fast as he could – I saw it "
"with my own eyes! Now Ditael is missing! I've come to you in secret to ask for "
"your help. Maybe you or one of your advisors could get to the bottom of this. My "
"Mistress would rather see the whole thing buried. After all, the sword that drove "
"him mad was meant for you...\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"나즈릴르 주인님이 너에게 줄 선물을 주기 위해 일하고 있어. 하지만 도제인 Ditael"
"이 너에게 주어야 할 무기를 쥐는 순간 미쳐버렸지. 그는 그것을 쥐고 도망가버렸어. 내 "
"두 눈으로 봤지! Ditael은 지금 실종되었어! 나는 도움을 청하기 위해 몰래 여기로 왔"
"어. 아마 네 조언자를 보내 도와줄 수도 있을 거야. 내 주인님은 이 소식이 퍼지지 않기"
"를 원해. 사람을 미치게 하는 검이 너에게 줄 선물이었으니까...\\\""

msgctxt "41ea1c5b-83a9-42e1-8525-d9e718673880"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf throws up his hands in fear.{/n} \\\"Not at all! She's the most "
"magnificent weaponsmith I've ever met in my entire life! I'm lucky she even "
"noticed me! She's made me so happy! I wish I weren't so stupid and clumsy, or I'd "
"be more worthy to help her! But I try as hard as I can.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프는 공포에 질려 손을 듭니다.{/n} \\\"아니야! 그녀는 내가 만나 본 대장장이 중 "
"최고야! 그녀를 만난 것도 행운이야! 나는 행복해! 내가 멍청하지 않았다면 그녀를 더 "
"잘 도울 수 있었을 텐데! 하지만 나는 최선을 다하고 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "71978651-454c-4666-b03d-58243e02245b"
msgid ""
"{n}Sartayne shrugs.{/n} \\\"I don't know. The Mistress said I couldn't touch it. "
"But I heard her ask Ditael to take it to you.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}Sartayne는 어깨를 들썩입니다.{/n} \\\"글쎄. 나는 만지면 안 된다고 했어. 하지만 "
"Ditael에게 부탁을 했지.\\\""

msgctxt "012f210f-8d20-4de9-b34d-a55f0a870c64"
msgid ""
"{n}The apprentice bows low and speaks as if reading a note.{/n} \\\"On behalf of "
"Mistress {d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d}, I would like to wish you eternal health and "
"express our gratitude for your kind protection.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}도제는 인사를 하고는 책을 읽듯이 말합니다.{/n} \\\"{d|Nazriel}Nazrielle{/d} 주인"
"님을 대신해서 네 보호에 감사로 너의 장수를 빈다고 했어.\\\""

msgctxt "05a72b22-9d68-4313-992d-2fb3845577e3"
msgid ""
"\\\"My Mistress wanted me to present you with this gift. She hopes that you would "
"be satisfied with it.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나보고 이 선물을 전하라고 했어. 그녀는 네가 만족하길 바라고 있어.\\\""

msgctxt "2c790c77-ce33-436d-a83c-1a7229fd8884"
msgid "{n}The elf bows low and vanishes silently.{/n}"
msgstr "{n}엘프는 인사하고 조용히 사라집니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "6852341f-a484-4e2e-a6c8-d33a3c6dd477"
msgid ""
"\\\"Oh... Oh no... This will make the Mistress very, very angry...\\\" {n}The elf "
"shrinks and backs away in fear.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"오... 오. 안 돼... 주인님이 화가 날 거야...\\\" {n}엘프는 몸을 움츠리고 공포에 "
"질려 물러납니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "52851a74-8f2e-4839-a160-f3851813acac"
msgid "\\\"I will give your order to the Mistress exactly as I hear it.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"내가 들은 대로 전할게.\\\""

msgctxt "f336c3e8-f4fe-41b4-9643-9c1662ca1411"
msgid "\\\"Mistress Nazrielle will hear your command, word for word.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나즈릴르 주인님에게 소식을 전할게.\\\""

msgctxt "b0215b25-d2f0-4729-8dc4-a56c11a3bbde"
msgid "Bog Mischief"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "a930788c-5133-47dc-b89e-93499fba84cf"
msgid "\\\"Run while you can!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"어서 도망가!\\\""

msgctxt "86a8075c-028c-495b-b8d9-bc92921f2ea6"
msgid "\\\"What the…\\\""
msgstr "\\\"도대체…\\\""

msgctxt "5d9bb77f-0eb0-4000-9577-ac9828b2136c"
msgid "\\\"Rise and shine! Get up, you lousy runts! Attack!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"어서 일어나! 멍청이들아! 공격해!\\\""

msgctxt "e0329210-610c-47b9-998b-f6abd81c7dcb"
msgid "\\\"Ohhh, my head…\\\""
msgstr "\\\"오... 머리야...\\\""

msgctxt "615e7497-2bf2-452a-a251-ead582e4a2fe"
msgid "\\\"Farewell, Ged.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"안녕히. Ged.\\\""

msgctxt "ba220c8e-def7-403d-ad4b-af54375c139c"
msgid "\\\"How did you end up here?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"어떻게 여기에 오게 되었지?\\\""

msgctxt "afa609a9-0cf9-438c-9a27-518404fcd5ec"
msgid ""
"\\\"Ahem… O fey! Thou art too cruel to the woeful creature, so conquered by thine "
"beauty! His heart is bleeding. He stands idly for all the day, staring into "
"loneliness. How can you ask his spirit not to sing, nor his knees to tremble at "
"your fair image? Deliver your mercy! Return to Kimiel, for no one can ever love "
"you as he!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"에헴... 페이야! 너의 아름다움에 매료된 불쌍한 생물에게 너무나 잔인하구나! 그의 "
"심장에서 피가 흐르고 있어. 그는 외로움에 묻혀 하루 종일 앉아만 있지. 네 모습을 보"
"고 무릎을 꿇고 너를 위해 노래하지 못하게 한다면 그건 너무 잔인해. 자비를 베풀어. 키"
"미엘에게 돌아가 누구도 너를 사랑하지 못하게 해다오!\\\""

msgctxt "07eb42ba-c092-4b8d-b834-8d9984fdfe41"
msgid ""
"Threatened to burn down the dryad's forest if she didn't accept Kimo's advances."
msgstr "그녀가 키모의 제안을 거부하다면 드라이어드의 숲을 불태우겠다고 협박합니다."

msgctxt "3f744f8a-0050-4f4b-b735-01ff42488873"
msgid ""
"\\\"Just keep going out with Kimo like before… or I'll burn down your precious "
"oak. And all the entire forest along with it.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"예전처럼 키모와 지내... 그렇지 않으면 네 소중한 오크나무들을 태워버리겠다. 모"
"든 숲을.\\\""

msgctxt "f16d9745-d629-42e3-aa82-0db27bf43aab"
msgid ""
"\\\"Kimo is a talented craftsman. But ever since you rejected him, he's lost all "
"inspiration. His gift is going to waste. Please, let him see you and talk to you – "
"at least in the name of art.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"키모는 타고난 장인이야. 하지만 네가 그를 거부한 이후로 그는 영감을 잃었어. 그"
"의 재능이 버려지고 있어. 부디 그와 만나줘. 그의 작품을 위해서라도.\\\""

msgctxt "5a71842a-a059-4386-9914-8917f43437e2"
msgid "\\\"Why have you rejected Kimo?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"왜 키모를 쫓아냈지?\\\""

msgctxt "b43e1ff3-b288-4101-8179-c3598423e768"
msgid "\\\"I'm done trying to persuade you. Farewell.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"너를 설득하는 것도 질렸어. 안녕히.\\\""

msgctxt "e250d72e-b06f-42d2-a3d6-bcfb59adfea9"
msgid ""
"{n}You recognize a dryad that you saw some time ago with a drunken satyr. Her skin "
"glistens like polished wood, and her head is crowned with a mane of grass and "
"leaves.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}당신은 이전에 술취한 사티어와 함께 있던 드라이어드를 발견했습니다. 그녀의 피부"
"는 빛났고 그녀는 머리에 풀과 나뭇잎으로 만든 왕관을 썼습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "89e18730-81f8-4750-9e62-793d176ab61c"
msgid ""
"\\\"Here you are! I knew you'd come to try and change my mind. Kimo talks about "
"you every day, you know.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"여기! 네가 와서 나를 설득할 거라는 걸 알고 있었지. 키모가 너에 대해 매일 얘기했"
"어.\\\""

msgctxt "6c432f7c-2bc8-4b3d-ad12-b011f71d073d"
msgid ""
"{n}The dryad pouts.{/n} \\\"No, no and no! I won't be with him, and that's that. "
"I'm tired and I want to be left alone. I'm done with this!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드라이어드가 뾰루퉁해집니다.{/n} \\\"아니야! 싫어! 나는 그와 함께하지 않을 거라"
"구. 나는 혼자 있고 싶어. 상관하지 않을래!\\\""

msgctxt "aebc2bfd-02c7-46d8-bc61-cdc2c37bf320"
msgid ""
"{n}The dryad covers her mouth in terror.{/n} \\\"No… I beg you, don't! I'll do "
"whatever you say… Tell him to come to me…\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드라이어드는 공포에 질려 입을 벌립니다.{/n} \\\"아니야... 부탁이야. 그러지 말아"
"줘! 말하는 대로 할게... 그가 와도 좋다고 전해줘...\\\""

msgctxt "afd8ecd8-6b59-4d99-a7a8-ff3d6fc67411"
msgid ""
"{n}The fey sighs and rolls her eyes.{/n} \\\"I am sick and tired of this! Why did "
"fate pick me to be sacrificed to art?\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}페이는 한숨을 쉬고 시선을 외면합니다.{/n} \\\"나는 이제 지쳤어! 왜 내 인생은 예"
"술에 희생해야 하는 거지?\\\""

msgctxt "338225c0-3793-4194-b456-39b0653c83a6"
msgid ""
"{n}The dryad is standing half-turned to you, hugging her shoulders with her arms. "
"At the end of your speech, she pats her eyes dry with a small oak leaf.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}드라이어드는 양 팔로 어깨를 감싼 채로 반쯤 몸을 돌려 당신을 봅니다. 당신의 말이 "
"끝나자 그녀는 작은 오크 나무 잎으로 눈물을 닦습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "14fcf68a-ae20-4e70-a779-15cbf62948b4"
msgid ""
"\\\"What do you mean, 'end up'? I live here. I grew up in this forest together "
"with my magnificent oak. If there's anyone who's 'ended up' here, it's you!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"무슨 말이야? 끝내다니? 나는 여기에 살아. 나는 오크 나무와 함께 여기서 자랐다"
"구. 여기를 끝내겠다니. 말도 안 돼!\\\""

msgctxt "5b91873d-20fd-4da2-90fd-e73d2a936c67"
msgid ""
"{n}The dryad shrugs.{/n} \\\"Maybe I just grew tired of him? I don't even know. "
"He's so… two-dimensional. There's no intrigue to him. Everything he does is so "
"predictable! All the flowers, all the compliments… I've had enough, thank you.\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}드라이어드는 어깨를 들썩입니다.{/n} \\\"아마 그에게 질려서 그런 걸까? 모르겠어. "
"그는... 이중적이야.  그가 하는 일은 모두 눈에 보여! 꽃과 달콤한 말... 나는 사양하겠"
"어.\\\""

msgctxt "6934acaf-f907-4653-99f4-89198ec32cd7"
msgid ""
"\\\"Oh well, you win. The artist can come back. It's not like I've got anything "
"better to do around here…\\\""
msgstr "\\\"좋아. 네가 이겼어. 그는 돌아와야 해. 여기에 있어봤자 좋은 게 없어...\\\""

msgctxt "301da0fc-2235-48f0-9ded-5108f282b6bf"
msgid ""
"\\\"O Shelyn! What do you do to us, you treacherous goddess? I know not myself "
"what arises in me. But hurry now, o messenger of love! Find Kimo at once and tell "
"him that his beloved cannot wait for his return.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"오. 쉘린! 도대체 우리에게 무슨 짓을 한 것인가? 내게 무슨 일이 일어났는지 몰랐"
"어. 나의 사랑을 어서 전해줘! 키모에게 전해서 나의 사랑이 당신을 기다린다고 말해줘."
"\\\""

msgctxt "1d7c2ac6-1d2a-4518-8df5-47e8f4a3281c"
msgid "{mf|Baron|Baroness|King|Queen} {name}, rightful ruler of these lands.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"{name}. 이 땅의 진정한 지배자.\\\""

msgctxt "52c52a60-7242-482b-888c-e142a757ecfe"
msgid "\\\"None of your business.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"네가 상관할 바 아니야.\\\""

msgctxt "9387af36-b657-48b9-b4c3-624960cac614"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"I didn't come here to talk. Die, scum!\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"너와 얘기하러 온 게 아니다. 쓰레기야!\\\""

msgctxt "877af9e9-dfc2-4fbd-9947-1409871ffb6a"
msgid "\\\"Why do keep upsetting the locals?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"왜 계속 주민들을 화나게 하지?\\\""

msgctxt "e5bcfccd-6197-4017-904b-937bb6e7dc83"
msgid ""
"[In a loud voice] \\\"I was just passing through when I saw you and I thought to "
"myself: 'why, I should come pay my respects!'\\\""
msgstr ""
"[큰 목소리로] \\\"나는 그냥 지나가던 사람이야. 그런데 심심해서 말하는 거야!\\\""

msgctxt "70a6406e-103d-4083-9776-da6a06b7c6f2"
msgid ""
"\\\"How can I persuade you to allow the villagers to live in peace, and depart "
"these lands for good?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"주민들을 괴롭히지 말고 이 땅을 떠나는 게 어때?\\\""

msgctxt "3e835459-3ac4-4e0c-a147-c1902dc01f76"
msgid "[Attack] \\\"You shouldn't have said that. Make peace with your gods!\\\""
msgstr "[공격] \\\"너는 말실수를 했어. 너의 신에게 가라!\\\""

msgctxt "9d1ed7c8-c134-41ee-9d93-4eab59022c20"
msgid "\\\"Leave, and never come back. I won't repeat myself.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"가서 다시는 돌아오지 마. 두번 말하지 않겠다.\\\""

msgctxt "35a5c16f-28ed-4abf-a2b6-cdd682e40462"
msgid "\\\"Wait. Are you talking about Kimo – the elven craftsman who's in love?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"잠깐. 사랑에 빠진 엘프 장인 키모?\\\""

msgctxt "37f3182e-1057-4c93-87f2-382624c6a2d4"
msgid "[Pass the bottle to the satyr] \\\"Here's your medicine.\\\""
msgstr "[사티어에게 병을 건넵니다] \\\"여기 네 약이다.\\\""

msgctxt "27856a9f-6057-4062-af03-6035f3a811b7"
msgid "\\\"What are you talking about?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"무슨 말하는 거야?\\\""

msgctxt "956850bc-fa02-4cae-bd6a-aa76a511e644"
msgid "\\\"I must go.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나는 가야 해.\\\""

msgctxt "9ef302b3-8ff5-4dc3-8bdf-80751abd1a3d"
msgid "\\\"Alright, alright. Sorry about that.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"좋아. 미안해.\\\""

msgctxt "60d8025d-7d59-451d-8bd3-f296e8fbc0e4"
msgid "[In an even louder voice] \\\"Huh?! You were saying?!\\\""
msgstr "[더 큰 목소리로] \\\"응?! 뭐라고?!\\\""

msgctxt "378ea938-1f70-481d-8cfb-5fe6ece5de91"
msgid "\\\"Whoops, sorry. I didn't mean to.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"오. 미안. 그러려던 건 아니었어.\\\""

msgctxt "af537c29-251a-478b-9043-a0af23b9cd6e"
msgid "[Screaming] \\\"What?! Why are you whispering?! Speak up, please!\\\""
msgstr "[비명] \\\"뭐?! 왜 속삭이는 거야?! 크게 말해!\\\""

msgctxt "3b4c52b9-488f-4382-98c2-f99828dbd2f5"
msgid ""
"{n}The foul, nauseating stench of morning-after breath permeates the glade. Fey of "
"all sizes and shapes litter the ground, sleeping on the grass side by side, some "
"of them scarcely clothed. A drowsy satyr squints in pain and shifts his heavy gaze "
"to you.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}아침에 일어난 직후의 입냄새가 납니다. 다양한 크기의 페이들이 바닥을 굴러다니거"
"나 자고 있고 몇몇은 거의 벗었습니다. 피곤해 보이는 사티어가 눈꺼풀을 천천히 들어 당"
"신을 봅니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "9bda499b-a92f-49f7-b775-28b3958b0f9d"
msgid "\\\"Curses… Who is it? Who's there?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"젠장... 누구야? 거기?\\\""

msgctxt "e3875c0a-caa7-43c1-8381-c4636c2ccbe7"
msgid ""
"{n}The satyr winces.{/n} \\\"Quiet, quiet, you hornless devil… What you want here?"
"\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}사티어가 찡그립니다.{/n} \\\"조용히 해. 이 뿔 없는 악마야... 무얼 원하는 거야?\\"
"\""

msgctxt "755fac67-8821-455b-88df-b118a3320848"
msgid ""
"\\\"Ha! I swear I could tell that just by looking at your puffed up chest… What "
"you want?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"하! 보기만 해도 나는 알 수 있어... 무얼 원해?\\\""

msgctxt "d9569628-e54b-4a87-814a-3cb83d1a6406"
msgid ""
"\\\"Some of them forget their place… We won't stand by whole some pointy-eared oaf "
"frolics with our girls!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"몇몇은 길을 잃어버렸지... 우리는 귀 뾰족한 망나니들이 우리 여자들과 있는 건 참"
"지 못해!\\\""

msgctxt "f6ac63da-48ce-4560-b0db-58e3199bc7bb"
msgid ""
"\\\"Ha! A midget {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen} of a midget country… What you want?"
"\\\""
msgstr "\\\"하! 멍청한 나라의 멍청한 지배자군... 무얼 원하지?\\\""

msgctxt "6de8e94f-9ee5-4395-8a7d-347350640ecd"
msgid ""
"\\\"Ha! With a muzzle like that? You could at least file the tusks down first… "
"What you want?\\\""
msgstr "\\\"하! 마음에 들지 않는군. 일단 진정하라고... 무얼 원해?\\\""

msgctxt "59f074db-732f-4e5b-afc8-c1e5e1f3cc27"
msgid ""
"{n}The satyr stares at you with an expression of pure agony on his face.{/n} \\"
"\"Ga-a-ah, what the hell. I couldn't care less about your damn villagers… My "
"head's splitting in two. Just bring me a drink. The poison is the cure, you know? "
"You bring me a drink, and I'll take the gang home. It's not like I'm ever going to "
"change her mind, that scatterbrain...\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}사티어는 분노로 당신을 봅니다.{/n} \\\"아악! 뭐야. 네 망할 주민들은 신경 쓰지 않"
"아... 머리가 너무 아프군. 마실 것 좀 줘. 치료의 물약 알지? 마실 것을 주면 그 망할 "
"녀석들을 보내주지. 내가 그녀의 마음을 바꿀 수 있을 것 같지는 않지만...\\\""

msgctxt "ccbca32d-7d24-48c9-83d7-dd6ce0483834"
msgid ""
"{n}The satyr hisses, covering his eyes with his hand:{/n} \\\"In the name of all "
"that's good and fair, lower your voice…\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}사티어는 손으로 얼굴을 덮으며 말합니다.{/n} \\\"제발 목소리 좀 낮춰...\\\""

msgctxt "556b8928-4653-4681-89aa-46b0ee7375ec"
msgid ""
"{n}The poor creature gives a weak moan.{/n} \\\"By the gods, why are you yelling "
"so loud…\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}그 불쌍한 생물은 신음합니다.{/n} \\\"오. 신이시여. 소리가 너무 크잖아...\\\""

msgctxt "7adb7271-f900-4e89-8fb5-e730a923ef6b"
msgid ""
"{n}Baring his teeth in a grin, the satyr reluctantly rises.{/n} \\\"Rise and "
"shine, you drunkards! We're going home!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}사티어는 씩 웃더니 일어섭니다.{/n} \\\"일어나! 이 주정뱅이들아! 집으로 가자!\\\""

msgctxt "ae3b6012-4181-4be5-8d50-45f88dd21710"
msgid ""
"{n}The satyr huffs a dull laugh.{/n} \\\"You're just full of yourself, aren't you?"
"\\\""
msgstr "{n}사티어가 멍청한 웃음을 짓습니다.{/n} \\\"그냥 혼잣말 하는 거지?\\\""

msgctxt "48ace223-d639-4b64-9b23-2143763cf2f3"
msgid ""
"\\\"Oh, you know him? How sweet. You can tell him he'll not be getting anywhere "
"with her. That sorry sack of stones doesn't need anyone except her tree…\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"오. 그를 알아? 귀엽군. 그녀와 함께 있다면 그는 조심해야 할 거야. 그 돌덩어리들"
"은 그녀의 나무 말고는 아무 쓸모가 없어...\\\""

msgctxt "eb0b3862-41f8-4e9f-9b57-0336291c5fe6"
msgid "\\\"Get lost, go talk to that elf of yours! See if I care!\\\""
msgstr "\\\"가서 네 엘프하고나 얘기해! 나는 상관하지 않아!\\\""

msgctxt "04e31880-81ab-4760-91f4-b02478556c8f"
msgid ""
"\\\"Huh, not bad… It's no fun playing tricks on those dim-witted farmers anyway. "
"Farewell, then. I'm not going to miss your face.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"흠. 나쁘지 않군... 그 멍청한 농부들을 괴롭히는 것도 재미 없어. 나는 가겠어. 네 "
"얼굴은 지겨워.\\\""

msgctxt "5b084d78-2d8e-415c-a56d-4d5b42b6b198"
msgid "\\\"You again…\\\""
msgstr "\\\"또 너냐…\\\""

msgctxt "5ceadbf5-0fde-487f-8d21-2c007b41e658"
msgid ""
"{n}The satyr waves at you dismissively.{/n} \\\"I'm not bowing to you. You've no "
"power over me…\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}사티어는 귀찮다는 듯 손을 흔듭니다.{/n} \\\"너에게는 인사하지 않아. 나는 네 종"
"이 아니야...\\\""

