msgctxt "0d46572a-8780-4678-a445-f7564c7b6358"
msgid ""
"\\\"You wanted to know if there was a place you could settle in around here...\\\""
msgstr "\\\"이 주변에서 정착할 수 있는지 내게 물었었지...?\\\""

msgctxt "ace01f0b-1940-4638-b294-3b80f499b941"
msgid ""
"{n}Before you is a tall, pale elf, the soft features of his face sharply "
"contrasting his angular figure. But his woeful gaze is fixed on the ground.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"{n}화난 표정과는 달리 부드러운 인상의 창백하고 키 큰 엘프가 당신 앞에 서있습니다. "
"하지만 그의 우울한 시선은 아래를 향해있습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "7ebb275c-b6f0-47e7-84dd-526925b10aa4"
msgid ""
"{n}He finally notices you and, startled, blinks at you absent-mindedly. He talks "
"slowly, slightly elongating his words as he speaks.{/n} \\\"Good day!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}그는 마침내 당신을 발견하고 멍하니 눈을 깜빡입니다. 그는 아주 천천히 말합니다.{/"
"n} \\\"안녕!\\\""

msgctxt "40f24427-dd69-4fac-bec9-2d2d6acff175"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf shrugs.{/n} \\\"My parents named me Kimiel. But my friends decided this "
"name didn't suit me so well…\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프가 어깨를 으쓱합니다.{/n} \\\"부모님이 내 이름을 키미엘이라고 지어주었지. 하"
"지만 친구들은 내 이름이 어울리지 않는다고 했어...\\\""

msgctxt "0891026c-3b05-4a10-8a99-10b1841b2d71"
msgid ""
"{n}The elf blushes ever so slightly and lowers his gaze.{/n} \\\"I… I can't tell "
"you. It's a secret!\\\""
msgstr ""
"{n}엘프의 얼굴이 붉어지고는 시선을 아래로 향합니다.{/n} \\\"나는... 말해줄 수 없"
"어. 비밀이야!\\\""

msgctxt "3d616b96-6191-427d-a947-f47aaffd6ac2"
msgid ""
"\\\"Although… if you promise…\\\" {n}The elf looks at you with hope in his eyes.{/"
"n} \\\"I'll tell you if you promise to help me!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"하지만... 네가 약속한다면...\\\" {n}엘프는 희망에 찬 눈빛으로 당신을 봅니다.{/"
"n} \\\"나를 돕겠다고 약속하면 말해줄게!\\\""

msgctxt "c0e2b8e0-f38c-48ec-9e75-523e961ea55c"
msgid ""
"\\\"Although... if you promise...\\\" {n}The elf looks at you with hope in his "
"eyes.{/n} \\\"If you promise to help me, then I will tell you!\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"하지만... 네가 약속한다면...\\\" {n}엘프는 희망에 찬 눈빛으로 당신을 봅니다.{/"
"n} \\\"나를 돕겠다고 약속하면 말해줄게!\\\""

msgctxt "b86d5d86-0f93-44fc-ad6d-38aa3f8dc769"
msgid ""
"\\\"My name is Kimo. Kimo Tavon.\\\" {n} With a wide smile, the elf slowly nods at "
"you.{/n}"
msgstr ""
"\\\"내 이름은 키모. 키모 타본이야.\\\" {n} 환하게 웃으며 엘프는 당신을 봅니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "4561625d-31b4-4687-b12b-15cba4eba111"
msgid ""
"\\\"Kimo. Kimo Tavon.\\\" {n} With a wide smile, the elf slowly nods at you.{/n}"
msgstr "\\\"키모. 키모 타본이야.\\\" {n} 환하게 웃으며 엘프는 당신을 봅니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "ac55e02d-ec6d-4d36-a3c5-5005f00022fb"
msgid ""
"\\\"That… that's the secret!\\\" {n}After some hesitation, the elf decides to add,"
"{/n} \\\"But it's not hard. Not at all! You have my word.\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"그건... 비밀이야!\\\" {n}엘프는 주저하다가 말합니다.{/n} \\\"하지만 그리 어렵"
