"{n}집중을 하자 엘프의 이마에 주름이 생깁니다.{/n} \\\"네가 그렇게 말한다면...\\\""

msgctxt "21e9bf06-2787-4606-a8fa-fb48a6421228"
msgid ""
"\\\"Nunuk the hunter told me that he saw an incredibly beautiful flower growing in "
"the swamp! I'd go and pick it myself, but I'm afraid I'd get lost... And there are "
"monsters there…\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"사냥꾼 누눅이 늪지에서 자라는 아주 예쁜 꽃을 발견했다고 했어! 거기 가서 꽃을 따"
"고 싶지만 길을 잃을까봐 겁나... 몬스터도 있고...\\\""

msgctxt "cd1916ef-7e62-411a-8742-37f224239358"
msgid ""
"\\\"Nunuk the hunter told me that he saw an incredibly beautiful flower growing in "
"the swamp! I would go and pick it myself, but I fear I would become lost. Also, "
"there are monsters there...\\\""
msgstr ""
"\\\"사냥꾼 누눅이 늪지에서 자라는 아주 예쁜 꽃을 발견했다고 했어! 거기 가서 꽃을 따"
"고 싶지만 길을 잃을까봐 겁나... 몬스터도 있고...\\\""

msgctxt "02581377-baa2-441c-a9d9-5be21c42de0c"
msgid ""
"\\\"Hm-m-m… In that case I… I'll give you my spear! I can make a lot of handy "
