"\\\"Yes?\\\" {n}The elf is so impatient that he's tying his fingers in a knot.{/n}"
msgstr "\\\"응?\\\" {n}엘프는 깍지를 끼고 눈이 빠지도록 기다리고 있었습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "d73a9294-8475-447f-bf93-86044cc2e2d8"
msgid "\\\"Yes?\\\" {n}The elf looks straight at you, his eyes wide.{/n}"
msgstr "\\\"응?\\\" {n}엘프는 눈을 크게 뜨고 당신을 보고 있습니다.{/n}"

msgctxt "20590dc9-2fe4-4ff6-86c7-163942ebef19"
msgid "\\\"How… how beautiful!\\\" {n}The elf reverently accepts the flower.{/n}"
