msgstr "\\\"그래…\\\""

msgctxt "733f8065-6523-4f19-8c99-77a31bd10393"
msgid "{n}The elf gives you a pensive look.{/n} \\\"Good day!\\\""
msgstr "{n}엘프는 당신을 경계하며 봅니다.{/n} \\\"안녕!\\\""

msgctxt "28774985-a86b-49d8-b39f-7d4ab148f3b2"
msgid ""
"\\\"Well, if you're offering this to me… than I gladly accept! It's a deal.\\\""
msgstr "\\\"나에게 제안을 한다면... 그럼 받아들일게! 약속했다.\\\""

msgctxt "43183aec-7231-41f8-9889-8f0f645a7d60"
msgid "A delicate flower with a faint sweet smell."
msgstr "달콤한 향기가 나는 한떨기 꽃입니다."

msgctxt "89a95263-099a-4038-9d05-b6ee46022949"
